na consulta pblica?</h2>\\n<p>Absolutament. Demaneu al responsable del vostre municipi o organitzaci que us doni els drets de perms necessaris per convertir-vos en moderador del projecte. Un cop concedits aquests permisos, pots configurar el teu propi projecte i cronologia i compartir la informaci que vulguis (vdeo, documents, imatges,...). Aix tamb us permetr convidar altres persones a la plataforma, cosa que els permetr publicar idees dins del vostre projecte, votar o comentar.</p>\\n<h2>Puc participar com a associaci/organitzaci/comit? </h2>\\n<p>S, aix s possible. Ats que noms el vostre nom i cognom sn visibles per als altres a la plataforma, noms podeu utilitzar el nom de la vostra organitzaci mentre configureu el vostre perfil.</p>\\n<h2>Per qu hauria d'utilitzar aquesta plataforma i no crear un lloc web jo mateix?</h2>\\n<p>Un equip de desenvolupadors dedicats i especialistes en participaci en lnia (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, encarregat pel vostre municipi o organitzaci) est millorant i actualitzant aquesta plataforma diriament. Fins i tot l'error ms petit s'aborda immediatament i, si teniu propostes creatives, us poden ajudar a assenyalar quines funcions de la plataforma es poden utilitzar per a aix o quines estan en procs.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Regla de separaci horitzontal\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Necessites ms informaci?</em></strong><em> Vols utilitzar la plataforma? Preguntes o comentaris? Poseu-vos en contacte amb el responsable del vostre municipi o organitzaci. O poseu-vos en contacte amb Go Vocal mitjanant <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "cy-GB": "<p>This <strong>all-in-one participation platform</strong> is an initiative of your municipality or organisation and can be used for different public consultation processes: collecting ideas, voting, discussing, surveys, polls, participatory budgeting, online mapping, scenario planning, support for advisory boards and committees, ...</p>\\n<p>On the home page, you'll see which <strong>processes are active </strong>and in which <strong>phase </strong>they currently are.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>How do I sign in on the platform?</h2>\\n<p>Signing in is done easily by giving your first and last name and your e-mail address. You could also use your Google or Facebook account. Only your first and last name will be visible to others.</p>\\n<h2>Can I use the platform myself, e.g. to organise a public consultation?</h2>\\n<p>Absolutely. Ask the responsible within your municipality or organisation to give you the needed permission rights to become a project moderator. Once granted these permissions, you can set up your own project and timeline and share the information you want (video, documents, images, ...). This will also allow you to invite others to the platform, enabling them to post ideas within your project, vote or comment.</p>\\n<h2>Can I participate as an association/organisation/committee? </h2>\\n<p>Yes, that's possible. Given that only your first and last name are visible to others on the platform, you can simply use your organisation's name while setting up your profile.</p>\\n<h2>Why would I use this platform and not create a website myself?</h2>\\n<p>A team of dedicated developers and specialists in online participation (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, commissioned by your municipality or organisation) is improving and updating this platform on a daily basis. Even the smallest bug gets tackled immediat