ign=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>How do I sign in on the platform?</h2>\\n<p>Signing in is done easily by giving your first and last name and your e-mail address. You could also use your Google or Facebook account. Only your first and last name will be visible to others.</p>\\n<h2>Can I use the platform myself, e.g. to organise a public consultation?</h2>\\n<p>Absolutely. Ask the responsible within your municipality or organisation to give you the needed permission rights to become a project moderator. Once granted these permissions, you can set up your own project and timeline and share the information you want (video, documents, images, ...). This will also allow you to invite others to the platform, enabling them to post ideas within your project, vote or comment.</p>\\n<h2>Can I participate as an association/organisation/committee? </h2>\\n<p>Yes, that's possible. Given that only your first and last name are visible to others on the platform, you can simply use your organisation's name while setting up your profile.</p>\\n<h2>Why would I use this platform and not create a website myself?</h2>\\n<p>A team of dedicated developers and specialists in online participation (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, commissioned by your municipality or organisation) is improving and updating this platform on a daily basis. Even the smallest bug gets tackled immediately and if you have creative proposals, they can help you pointing out which features of the platform can be used for this or which ones are in the pipeline.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Need more information?</em></strong><em> Do you want to use the platform? Questions or feedback? Contact the responsible within your municipality or organisation. Or contact Go Vocal through <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "en-GB": "<p>This <strong>all-in-one participation platform</strong> is an initiative of your municipality or organisation and can be used for different public consultation processes: collecting ideas, voting, discussing, surveys, polls, participatory budgeting, online mapping, scenario planning, support for advisory boards and committees, ...</p>\\n<p>On the home page, you'll see which <strong>processes are active </strong>and in which <strong>phase </strong>they currently are.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>How do I sign in on the platform?</h2>\\n<p>Signing in is done easily by giving your first and last name and your e-mail address. You could also use your Google or Facebook account. Only your first and last name will be visible to others.</p>\\n<h2>Can I use the platform myself, e.g. to organise a public consultation?</h2>\\n<p>Absolutely. Ask the responsible within your municipality or organisation to give you the needed permission rights to become a project moderator. Once granted these permissions, you can set up your own project and timeline and share the information you want (video, documents, images, ...). This will also allow you to invite others to the platform, enabling them to post ideas within your project, vote or comment.</p>\\n<h2>Can I participate as an association/organisation/committee? </h2>\\n<p>Yes, that's possible. Given that only your first and last name are visible to others on the platform, you can simply use your organisation's name while setting up your profile.</p>\\n<h2>Why would I use this platform and not create a website myself?</h2>\\n<p>A team of dedicated developers and specialists in online participation (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, commissioned by your municipality or organisation) is improving and updating this platform on a daily basis. Even the smallest bug gets tackled immediately and if you have creative proposals, they can help you pointing out which features of the platform can be used for this or which ones are in the pipeline.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Need more information?</em></strong><em> Do you want to use the platform? Questions or feedback? Contact the responsible within your municipality or organisation. Or contact Go Vocal through <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "en-IE": "<p>This <strong>all-in-one participation platform</strong> is an initiative of your municipality or organisation and can be used for different public consultation processes: collecting ideas, voting, discussing, surveys, polls, participatory budgeting, online mapping, scenario planning, support for advisory boards and committees, ...</p>\\n<p>On the home page, you'll see which <strong>processes are active </strong>and in which <strong>phase </strong>they currently are.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>How do I sign in on the platform?</h2>\\n<p>Signing in is done easily by giving your first and last name and your e-mail address. You could also use your Google or Facebook account. Only your first and last name will be visible to others.</p>\\n<h2>Can I use the platform myself, e.g. to organise a public consultation?</h2>\\n<p>Absolutely. Ask the responsible within your municipality or organisation to give you the needed permission rights to become a project moderator. Once granted these permissions, you can set up your own project and timeline and share the information you want (video, documents, images, ...). This will also allow you to invite others to the platform, enabling them to post ideas within your project, vote or comment.</p>\\n<h2>Can I participate as an association/organisation/committee? </h2>\\n<p>Yes, that's possible. Given that only your first and last name are visible to others on the platform, you can simply use your organisation's name while setting up your profile.</p>\\n<h2>Why would I use this platform and not create a website myself?</h2>\\n<p>A team of dedicated developers and specialists in online participation (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, commissioned by your municipality or organisation) is improving and updating this platform on a daily basis. Even the smallest bug gets tackled immediately and if you have creative proposals, they can help you pointing out which features of the platform can be used for this or which ones are in the pipeline.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Need more information?</em></strong><em> Do you want to use the platform? Questions or feedback? Contact the responsible within your municipality or organisation. Or contact Go Vocal through <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "es-CL": "Descubre ms informacin relacionada con la plataforma.", "es-ES": "Descubre ms informacin relacionada con la plataforma.", "fi-FI": "<p>This <strong>all-in-one participation platform</strong> is an initiative of your municipality or organisation and can be used for different public consultation processes: collecting ideas, voting, discussing, surveys, polls, participatory budgeting, online mapping, scenario planning, support for advisory boards and committees, ...</p>\\n<p>On the home page, you'll see which <strong>processes are active </strong>and in which <strong>phase </strong>they currently are.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>How do I sign in on the platform?</h2>\\n<p>Signing in is done easily by giving your first and last name and your e-mail address. You could also use your Google or Facebook account. Only your first and last name will be visible to others.</p>\\n<h2>Can I use the platform myself, e.g. to organise a public consultation?</h2>\\n<p>Absolutely. Ask the responsible within your municipality or organisation to give you the needed permission rights to become a project moderator. Once granted these permissions, you can set up your own project and timeline and share the information you want (video, documents, images, ...). This will also allow you to invite others to the platform, enabling them to post ideas within your project, vote or comment.</p>\\n<h2>Can I participate as an association/organisation/committee? </h2>\\n<p>Yes, that's possible. Given that only your first and last name are visible to others on the platform, you can simply use your organisation's name while setting up your profile.</p>\\n<h2>Why would I use this platform and not create a website myself?</h2>\\n<p>A team of dedicated developers and specialists in online participation (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, commissioned by your municipality or organisation) is improving and updating this platform on a daily basis. Even the smallest bug gets tackled immediately and if you have creative proposals, they can help you pointing out which features of the platform can be used for this or which ones are in the pipeline.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Need more information?</em></strong><em> Do you want to use the platform? Questions or feedback? Contact the responsible within your municipality or organisation. Or contact Go Vocal through <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "fr-BE": "<p>Ceci est une <strong>plateforme de participation</strong>  l'initiative de votre municipalit ou de votre organisation. Elle peut tre utilise pour diffrents processus de consultations publics : via une collecte d'ides, un vote, des discussions, un sondage, une enqute, un budget participatif, une cartographie interactive, un choix entre plusieurs scenarios, un soutien pour les conseils communaux, municipaux, ou les comits, etc.</p>\\n<p>Sur la page d'accueil, vous verrez quels sont <strong>les processus actifs</strong> et dans quelle <strong>phase</strong> ils se trouvent actuellement.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"7b81cbc6-1e22-4511-b96d-867392471bcb\\" alt=\\"Ligne de sparation horizontale\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>Comment puis-je me connecter sur la plateforme ?</h2>\\n<p>Il est trs simple de s'inscrire en entrant son nom, prnom et adresse e-mail. vous pouvez galement utiliser votre compte Google ou Facebook. Seulement vos nom et prnom seront visibles pour les autres utilisateurs.</p>\\n<h2>Puis-je utiliser la plateforme moi-mme, pour organiser une consultation publique par exemple ?</h2>\\n<p>Absolument. Demandez au responsable de votre commune ou de organisation de vous donner les droits ncessaires pour devenir un modrateur de projet. Une fois obtenus, vous pouvez crer votre propre projet et ligne de temps, et partager l'information que vous dsirez (vidos, documents, images, etc.) Cela vous donnera galement la possibilit d'inviter d'autres utilisateurs sur la plateforme, de leur permettre de poster des ides au sein de votre projet, ou bien de voter et commenter.</p>\\n<h2>Puis-je participer en tant qu'association, organisation, comit ?</h2>\\n<p>Oui, c'est possible. Puisque seul le nom et le prnom de l'utilisateur sont visibles aux autres sur la plateforme, vous pouvez simplement utiliser le nom de votre organisation lors de la cration de votre profil.</p>\\n<h2>Pourquoi devrais-je utiliser cette plateforme au lieu de crer un site moi-mme ?</h2>\\n<p>Une quipe de dveloppeurs et de spcialistes de la participation en ligne (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/fr\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, commissionn par votre commune ou votre organisation) amliore et met  jour cette plateforme au quotidien. Chaque bug notifi est rsolu immdiatement et si vous avez des propositions cratives, ils peuvent vous aider en vous indiquant quelles fonctionnalits sont les plus adaptes ou lesquelles sont sur le point de sortir.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"02896ca6-6155-4829-8aee-0d1a65fa6193\\" alt=\\"Ligne de sparation horizontale\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Besoin de plus dinformations ? </em></strong><em>Envie dutiliser la plateforme ? Une question ou un commentaire ? Contactez le responsable de votre commune ou organisation. Ou contactez le support de Go Vocal via <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p>", "fr-FR": "<p>Ceci est une <strong>plateforme de participation</strong>  l'initiative de votre municipalit ou de votre organisation. Elle peut tre utilise pour diffrents processus de consultations publics : via une collecte d'ides, un vote, des discussions, un sondage, une enqute, un budget participatif, une cartographie interactive, un choix entre plusieurs scenarios, un soutien pour les conseils communaux, municipaux, ou les comits, etc.</p>\\n<p>Sur la page d'accueil, vous verrez quels sont <strong>les processus actifs</strong> et dans quelle <strong>phase</strong> ils se trouvent actuellement.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"7b81cbc6-1e22-4511-b96d-867392471bcb\\" alt=\\"Ligne de sparation horizontale\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>Comment puis-je me connecter sur la plateforme ?</h2>\\n<p>Il est trs simple de s'inscrire en entrant son nom, prnom et adresse e-mail. vous pouvez galement utiliser votre compte Google ou Facebook. Seulement vos nom et prnom seront visibles pour les autres utilisateurs.</p>\\n<h2>Puis-je utiliser la plateforme moi-mme, pour organiser une consultation publique par exemple ?</h2>\\n<p>Absolument. Demandez au responsable de votre commune ou de organisation de vous donner les droits ncessaires pour devenir un modrateur de projet. Une fois obtenus, vous pouvez crer votre propre projet et ligne de temps, et partager l'information que vous dsirez (vidos, documents, images, etc.) Cela vous donnera galement la possibilit d'inviter d'autres utilisateurs sur la plateforme, de leur permettre de poster des ides au sein de votre projet, ou bien de voter et commenter.</p>\\n<h2>Puis-je participer en tant qu'association, organisation, comit ?</h2>\\n<p>Oui, c'est possible. Puisque seul le nom et le prnom de l'utilisateur sont visibles aux autres sur la plateforme, vous pouvez simplement utiliser le nom de votre organisation lors de la cration de votre profil.</p>\\n<h2>Pourquoi devrais-je utiliser cette plateforme au lieu de crer un site moi-mme ?</h2>\\n<p>Une quipe de dveloppeurs et de spcialistes de la participation en ligne (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/fr\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, commissionn par votre commune ou votre organisation) amliore et met  jour cette plateforme au quotidien. Chaque bug notifi est rsolu immdiatement et si vous avez des propositions cratives, ils peuvent vous aider en vous indiquant quelles fonctionnalits sont les plus adaptes ou lesquelles sont sur le point de sortir.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"02896ca6-6155-4829-8aee-0d1a65fa6193\\" alt=\\"Ligne de sparation horizontale\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Besoin de plus dinformations ? </em></strong><em>Envie dutiliser la plateforme ? Une question ou un commentaire ? Contactez le responsable de votre commune ou organisation. Ou contactez le support de Go Vocal via <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p>", "hr-HR": "<p>Ova <strong>sveobuhvatna platforma za sudjelovanje</strong> inicijativa je vae opine ili organizacije i moe se koristiti za razliite procese javnih konzultacija: prikupljanje ideja, glasovanje, rasprave, upitnike, ankete, skupno odreivanje prorauna, mapiranje na mrei, planiranje scenarija, podrku za savjetodavne odbore i komisije, ...</p>\\n<p>Na poetnoj stranici vidjet ete koji su <strong>procesi aktivni </strong>i u kojoj se <strong>fazi </strong>trenutano nalaze.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>Kako se mogu prijaviti na platformu?</h2>\\n<p>Prijava je jednostavna tako da unesete svoje ime i prezime te svoju adresu e-pote. Takoer moete koristiti svoj Google ili Facebook raun. Drugima e biti vidljivi samo vae ime i prezime.</p>\\n<h2>Mogu li sam koristiti platformu, npr. organizirati javno savjetovanje?</h2>\\n<p>Apsolutno. Zamolite odgovorne u vaoj opini ili organizaciji da vam daju potrebna prava za doputenje da postanete moderator projekta. Nakon to dobijete ta doputenja, moete postaviti vlastiti projekt i vremenski okvir te dijeliti informacije koje elite (videozapise, dokumente, slike, ...). To e vam takoer omoguiti da pozovete druge na platformu, omoguujui im da objavljuju ideje unutar vaeg projekta, glasaju ili komentiraju.</p>\\n<h2>Mogu li sudjelovati kao udruga/organizacija/odbor? </h2>\\n<p>Da, to je mogue. S obzirom da su samo vae ime i prezime vidljivi drugima na platformi, moete jednostavno koristiti naziv svoje organizacije dok postavljate svoj profil.</p>\\n<h2>Zato da koristim ovu platformu, a ne da sam napravim web-mjesto?</h2>\\n<p>Tim predanih programera i strunjaka za online sudjelovanje (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, naruila vaa opina ili organizacija) poboljava i aurira ovu platformu na dnevnoj bazi. ak i najmanja pogreka rjeava se odmah, a ako imate kreativne prijedloge, oni vam mogu pomoi da istaknu koje se znaajke platforme mogu koristiti za to ili koje su u pripremi.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Trebate vie informacija?</em></strong><em> elite li koristiti platformu? Imate pitanja ili povratne informacije? Obratite se odgovornom u vaoj opini ili organizaciji. Ili kontaktirajte Go Vocal putem <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "hu-HU": "<p>This <strong>all-in-one participation platform</strong> is an initiative of your municipality or organisation and can be used for different public consultation processes: collecting ideas, voting, discussing, surveys, polls, participatory budgeting, online mapping, scenario planning, support for advisory boards and committees, ...</p>\\n<p>On the home page, you'll see which <strong>processes are active </strong>and in which <strong>phase </strong>they currently are.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>How do I sign in on the platform?</h2>\\n<p>Signing in is done easily by giving your first and last name and your e-mail address. You could also use your Google or Facebook account. Only your first and last name will be visible to others.</p>\\n<h2>Can I use the platform myself, e.g. to organise a public consultation?</h2>\\n<p>Absolutely. Ask the responsible within your municipality or organisation to give you the needed permission rights to become a project moderator. Once granted these permissions, you can set up your own project and timeline and share the information you want (video, documents, images, ...). This will also allow you to invite others to the platform, enabling them to post ideas within your project, vote or comment.</p>\\n<h2>Can I participate as an association/organisation/committee? </h2>\\n<p>Yes, that's possible. Given that only your first and last name are visible to others on the platform, you can simply use your organisation's name while setting up your profile.</p>\\n<h2>Why would I use this platform and not create a website myself?</h2>\\n<p>A team of dedicated developers and specialists in online participation (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, commissioned by your municipality or organisation) is improving and updating this platform on a daily basis. Even the smallest bug gets tackled immediately and if you have creative proposals, they can help you pointing out which features of the platform can be used for this or which ones are in the pipeline.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Need more information?</em></strong><em> Do you want to use the platform? Questions or feedback? Contact the responsible within your municipality or organisation. Or contact Go Vocal through <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "it-IT": "<p>Questa <strong>piattaforma di partecipazione all-in-one</strong>  un'iniziativa del vostro comune o organizzazione e pu essere utilizzata per diversi processi di consultazione pubblica: raccolta di idee, votazione, discussione, sondaggi, sondaggi, bilancio partecipativo, mappatura online, pianificazione di scenari, supporto per consigli e comitati consultivi, ...</p>\\n<p>Nella home page, potrete vedere quali <strong>processi sono attivi </strong>e in quale <strong>fase </strong>sono attualmente.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>Come si accede alla piattaforma?</h2>\\n<p>L'accesso si fa facilmente dando il proprio nome, cognome e indirizzo e-mail. Potete anche usare il vostro account Google o Facebook. Solo il vostro nome e cognome saranno visibili agli altri.</p>\\n<h2>Posso usare la piattaforma da solo, ad esempio per organizzare una consultazione pubblica?</h2>\\n<p>Assolutamente. Chiedete al responsabile del vostro comune o della vostra organizzazione di darvi i permessi necessari per diventare un moderatore del progetto. Una volta concessi questi permessi, puoi impostare il tuo progetto e la tua linea temporale e condividere le informazioni che vuoi (video, documenti, immagini, ...). Questo vi permetter anche di invitare altri alla piattaforma, permettendo loro di postare idee all'interno del vostro progetto, votare o commentare.</p>\\n<h2>Posso partecipare come associazione/organizzazione/comitato? </h2>\\n<p>S,  possibile. Dato che solo il vostro nome e cognome sono visibili agli altri sulla piattaforma, potete semplicemente usare il nome della vostra organizzazione mentre impostate il vostro profilo.</p>\\n<h2>Perch dovrei usare questa piattaforma e non creare un sito web?</h2>\\n<p>Un team di sviluppatori dedicati e specialisti nella partecipazione online (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, commissionato dal vostro comune o organizzazione) sta migliorando e aggiornando questa piattaforma su base giornaliera. Anche il pi piccolo bug viene affrontato immediatamente e se avete proposte creative, possono aiutarvi indicandovi quali caratteristiche della piattaforma possono essere utilizzate per questo o quali sono in cantiere.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Servono altre informazioni?</em></strong><em> Vuoi utilizzare la piattaforma? Domande o feedback? Contatta il responsabile del tuo comune o della tua organizzazione. Oppure contatta Go Vocal attraverso <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "kl-GL": "Oplev mere information relateret til platformen.", "lb-LU": "<p>Ds<strong> All-In-One-Bedeelegungsplattform</strong> ass eng Initiativ vun rer Gemeng oder Organisatioun a ka fir verschidden ffentlech Consultatioune genotzt ginnn: Iddie sammelen, Ofstmmungen, Disskussiounen, mfroen, Enquten, Biergerbudget, Online-Mapping, Planifikatioun vu Szenarien, nnersttzung vun berodend Gremien a Kommitteen,...</p>\\n<p>Op der Homapage gesitt Dir, wat fir <strong>Prozesser aktiv sinn </strong> an a wat fir enger<strong>Phas </strong>si am Moment sinn.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>Wi mellt Dir Iech op der Plattformm un?</h2>\\n<p>Umelle kann ee sech einfach, andeem ee si Vir- an Nonumm a seng E-Mail-Adress ugtt. Dir knnt och re Facebook- oder Google-Kont benotzen. Nmmen re Vir- an Nonumm ass fir aner Persoune siichtbar.</p>\\n<h2>Kann ech d'Plattform selwer benotzen, fir z.B. eng ffentlech Consultatioun ze organisieren?</h2>\\n<p>Absolutt. Frot di responsabel Persoun an rer Gemeng oder Organisatioun no der erfuerderlecher Geneemegung, fir e Projetsmoderator ze ginn. Esoubal Dir ds Geneemegung hutt, knnt Dir ren eegene Projet an Timeline uleen an di Informatiounen deelen, di Dir wllt (Video, Dokumenter, Biller, ...). Dat erlaabt et Iech och, aner Persounen op d'Plattform ze invitieren, sou datt si Iddien an re Projet posten, ofstmmen oder kommentiere knnen.</p>\\n<h2>Kann ech och als Verin/Organisatioun/Kommitee deelhuelen?</h2>\\n<p>Jo, dat ass miglech. Well nmmen re Vir- an Nonumm fir aner Persounen op der Plattform siichtbar sinn, knnt Dir einfach den Numm vun rer Organisatioun benotzen, fir re Profil unzeleen.</p>\\n<h2>Firwat sollt ech ds Plattform benotzen an net selwer e Site uleen?</h2>\\n<p>En Team vun egagierten Entwckler a Spezialisten an der Online-Bedeelegung (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>,, di vun rer Gemeng beoptragt goufen) verbessert an aktualisiert ds Plattfor all Dag. Esouguer dee klengste Feeler gtt direkt an Ugrff geholl, a wann Dir kreativ Propositioune kritt, hllefen se Iech, ze verstoen, wat fir Funktionen op der Plattform dofir gebraucht knne ginn oder an der Virbereedung sinn.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Dir braucht mi Informatiounen?</em></strong><em>Wllt Dir d'Plattform notzen? Froen oder Feedback? Kontaktiert di responsabel Persoun an rer Gemeng oder Organisatioun. Oder kontaktiert Go Vocal nner <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "lt-LT": "<p>i <strong>\\"viskas viename\\" dalyvavimo platforma</strong> yra js savivaldybs ar organizacijos iniciatyva ir gali bti naudojama vairiems viej konsultacij procesams: idj rinkimui, balsavimui, diskusijoms, apklausoms, apklausoms, dalyvaujamojo biudeto sudarymui, internetiniam emlapi sudarymui, scenarij planavimui, patariamj taryb ir komitet palaikymui, ...</p>\\n<p>Pagrindiniame puslapyje matysite, kurie <strong>procesai yra aktyvs </strong>ir kuriame <strong>etape </strong>jie iuo metu yra.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>Kaip prisijungti prie platformos?</h2>\\n<p>Prisijungti galima paprastai, nurodius savo vard, pavard ir el. pato adres. Taip pat galite naudoti savo \\"Google\\" arba \\"Facebook\\" paskyr. Kitiems bus matomas tik js vardas ir pavard.</p>\\n<h2>Ar galiu pats naudotis platforma, pavyzdiui, organizuoti viesias konsultacijas?</h2>\\n<p>inoma. Papraykite, kad js savivaldybs ar organizacijos atsakingas asmuo suteikt jums reikiamas teises, kad galtumte tapti projekto moderatoriumi. Gav ias teises, galite sukurti savo projekt ir laiko juost bei dalytis norima informacija (vaizdo raais, dokumentais, nuotraukomis...). Taip pat galsite pakviesti kitus asmenis  platform, kad jie galt skelbti js projekto idjas, balsuoti ar komentuoti.</p>\\n<h2>Ar galiu dalyvauti kaip asociacija / organizacija / komitetas? </h2>\\n<p>Taip, tai manoma. Atsivelgiant  tai, kad platformoje kitiems matomi tik js vardas ir pavard, kurdami savo profil galite tiesiog naudoti savo organizacijos pavadinim.</p>\\n<h2>Kodl turiau naudotis ia platforma, o ne pats susikurti svetain?</h2>\\n<p>Js savivaldybs ar organizacijos usakymu i platform kasdien tobulina ir atnaujina atsidavusi krj ir dalyvavimo internete specialist komanda<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">(\\"Go Vocal\\"</a>). Net menkiausia klaida nedelsiant paalinama, o jei turite krybini pasilym, jie gali jums padti nurodydami, kokias platformos funkcijas galima tam panaudoti arba kokios funkcijos yra rengiamos.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Reikia daugiau informacijos?</em></strong><em> Norite naudotis platforma? Turite klausim ar atsiliepim? Kreipkits  savo savivaldybs ar organizacijos atsakingus asmenis. Arba susisiekite su \\"Go Vocal\\" per <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "lv-LV": "<p> <strong>daudzfunkciju ldzdalbas platforma</strong> ir jsu pavaldbas vai organizcijas iniciatva, un to var izmantot dadiem sabiedrisks apsprieanas procesiem: ideju vkanai, balsoanai, diskusijm, aptaujm, apsekojumiem, ldzdalbas budeta veidoanai, tiesaistes kartanai, scenriju plnoanai, konsultatvo padomju un komiteju atbalstam, ...</p>\\n<p>Skumlap js redzsiet, kuri <strong>procesi ir aktvi </strong>un kur <strong>posm </strong>tie palaik atrodas </p> \\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>K pierakstties platform?</h2>\\n<p>Pierakstans notiek vienkri, nordot savu vrdu, uzvrdu un e-pasta adresi. Js varat izmantot ar savu Google vai Facebook kontu. Prjiem bs redzams tikai jsu vrds un uzvrds </p>.\\n<h2>Vai es pats varu izmantot platformu, piemram, lai organiztu sabiedrisko apsprieanu?</h2>\\n<p>Protams. Ldziet atbildgo personu sav pavaldb vai organizcij pieirt jums nepiecieams ataujas tiesbas, lai ktu par projekta moderatoru. Pc o tiesbu pieiranas js varat izveidot savu projektu un laika grafiku un kopgot informciju (video, dokumentus, attlus u. c.). Tas aus jums ar uzaicint citus dalbniekus piedalties platform, aujot viiem publict idejas jsu projekt, balsot vai komentt.</p>\\n<h2> Vai es varu piedalties k asocicija/organizcija/komiteja? </h2>\\n<p>Ja, tas ir iespjams. emot vr, ka citiem platform ir redzams tikai jsu vrds un uzvrds, veidojot savu profilu, js varat vienkri izmantot savas organizcijas nosaukumu </p>.\\n<h2>Kpc man vajadztu izmantot o platformu, nevis paam izveidot tmeka vietni?</h2>\\n<p>o platformu ik dienu uzlabo un atjaunina pau izstrdtju un tiesaistes ldzdalbas specilistu komanda (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, kuras pasttjs ir jsu pavaldba vai organizcija). Pat mazk kda tiek nekavjoties novrsta, un, ja jums ir radoi prieklikumi, vii var jums paldzt, nordot, kuras funkcijas var izmantot im nolkam vai kuras funkcijas atrodas izstrdanas stadij.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Vai nepiecieama papildu informcija?</em></strong><em>Vai vlaties izmantot platformu? Jautjumi vai atsauksmes? Sazinieties ar atbildgo personu sav pavaldb vai organizcij. Vai sazinieties ar Go Vocal, izmantojot <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "nb-NO": "<p>Denne <strong>alt-i-ett-plattformen for medvirkning</strong> er et initiativ fra din kommune eller organisasjon og kan brukes til ulike offentlige hringsprosesser: innsamling av ideer, stemmegivning, diskusjon, sprreunderskelser, avstemninger, deltakende budsjettering, kartlegging p nett, scenarioplanlegging, sttte til rdgivende rd og utvalg, ...</p>\\n<p>P hjemmesiden kan du se hvilke <strong>prosesser som er aktive </strong>og i hvilken <strong>fase </strong>de befinner seg i.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>Hvordan logger jeg meg p plattformen?</h2>\\n<p>Du logger deg enkelt inn ved  oppgi for- og etternavn og e-postadresse. Du kan ogs bruke Google- eller Facebook-kontoen din. Bare for- og etternavnet ditt vil vre synlig for andre.</p>\\n<h2>Kan jeg bruke plattformen selv, f.eks. for  organisere en offentlig hring?</h2>\\n<p>Ja, absolutt. Be den ansvarlige i kommunen eller organisasjonen din om  gi deg de ndvendige rettighetene for  bli prosjektmoderator. Nr du har ftt disse rettighetene, kan du sette opp ditt eget prosjekt og din egen tidslinje og dele den informasjonen du nsker (video, dokumenter, bilder, ...). Da kan du ogs invitere andre til plattformen, slik at de kan legge ut ideer i prosjektet ditt, stemme eller kommentere.</p>\\n<h2>Kan jeg delta som en forening/organisasjon/komit? </h2>\\n<p>Ja, det er mulig. Ettersom det bare er for- og etternavnet ditt som er synlig for andre p plattformen, kan du bare bruke organisasjonens navn nr du oppretter profilen din.</p>\\n<h2>Hvorfor skal jeg bruke denne plattformen i stedet for  lage en nettside selv?</h2>\\n<p>Et team av dedikerte utviklere og spesialister p nettdeltakelse<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">(Go Vocal</a>, p oppdrag fra din kommune eller organisasjon) forbedrer og oppdaterer denne plattformen hver dag. Selv den minste feil blir rettet umiddelbart, og hvis du har kreative forslag, kan de hjelpe deg med  peke ut hvilke funksjoner i plattformen som kan brukes til dette, eller hvilke som er p trappene.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Trenger du mer informasjon?</em></strong><em> nsker du  bruke plattformen? Har du sprsml eller tilbakemeldinger? Kontakt den ansvarlige i din kommune eller organisasjon. Eller kontakt Go Vocal via <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "nl-BE": "<p>Dit <strong>all-in-one participatieplatform</strong> is een initiatief van jouw gemeente of organisatie en kan worden ingezet voor allerhande inspraakprocessen: ideen ophalen, stemmen, discussiren, enqutes, polls, burgerbegroting, openbare onderzoeken, online mapping, scenarioplanning, ondersteuning voor adviesraden en comits, etc.</p>\\n<p>Op de homepagina zie je welke <strong>processen actief</strong> zijn of in welke <strong>fase</strong> een proces zich bevindt.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"27345c70-4967-48e6-a6ba-430dde6eeffb\\" alt=\\"Horizontale scheidingsregel\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>Hoe log ik in op het platform?</h2>\\n<p>Inloggen kan eenvoudig door je aan te melden met je voornaam, naam en e-mailadres. Je kunt ook je Google- of Facebook-account gebruiken. Enkel je naam en voornaam is zichtbaar voor anderen.</p>\\n<h2>Kan ik het platform zelf gebruiken, bijvoorbeeld om een inspraaktraject op te zetten?</h2>\\n<p>Dat kan zeker. Vraag aan de verantwoordelijke persoon binnen jouw gemeente of organisatie om jou de nodige toegangsrechten te geven om van jou een projectmoderator te maken. Je kunt dan zelf je project en tijdslijn opzetten en de nodige informatie (video, documenten, afbeeldingen, ) delen. Ook kan je dan zelf anderen op het platform uitnodigen, waardoor ze binnen jouw project ideen kunnen posten, of stemmen en reageren op bestaande ideen.</p>\\n<h2>Kan ik als vereniging/organisatie/comit deelnemen?</h2>\\n<p>Ja, dat kan. Omdat voor andere gebruikers van het platform enkel je voornaam en naam zichtbaar is, vul je binnen je profiel dus gewoon de naam van je vereniging in. Bvb. naam: <em>vzw</em> en voornaam: <em>De Globetrotters</em>. Ongeacht je e-mailadres, zien andere mensen enkel <em>vzw De Globetrotters</em>.</p>\\n<h2>Waarom zou ik dit platform gebruiken en niet zelf een website maken?</h2>\\n<p>Een team van gedreven developers en specialisten in online participatie (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, in opdracht van jouw gemeente of organisatie) is dagelijks bezig met dit platform te verbeteren en te updaten. De kleinste bug wordt direct aangepakt en als je zelf creatieve voorstellen hebt, kunnen we je zeggen welke toepassingen van het platform je hiervoor kunt gebruiken of welke er in de pijplijn zitten.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"4d291006-0414-4f93-903b-fb911a00d510\\" alt=\\"Horizontale scheidingsregel\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Meer informatie nodig? </em></strong><em>Wil je het platform gebruiken? Vragen of feedback? Contacteer de verantwoordelijke dienst of persoon van je gemeente of organisatie of neem contact met Go Vocal via <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a></em></p><strong></strong>", "nl-NL": "<p>Dit <strong>all-in-one participatieplatform</strong> is een initiatief van jouw gemeente of organisatie en kan worden ingezet voor allerhande inspraakprocessen: ideen ophalen, stemmen, discussiren, vragenlijsten, polls, burgerbegroting, openbare onderzoeken, online mapping, scenarioplanning, ondersteuning voor adviesraden en comits, etc.</p>\\n<p>Op de homepagina zie je welke <strong>processen actief</strong> zijn of in welke <strong>fase</strong> een proces zich bevindt.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"27345c70-4967-48e6-a6ba-430dde6eeffb\\" alt=\\"Horizontale scheidingsregel\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>Hoe log ik in op het platform?</h2>\\n<p>Inloggen kan eenvoudig door je aan te melden met je voornaam, naam en e-mailadres. Je kunt ook je Google- of Facebook-account gebruiken. Enkel je naam en voornaam is zichtbaar voor anderen.</p>\\n<h2>Kan ik het platform zelf gebruiken, bijvoorbeeld om een inspraaktraject op te zetten?</h2>\\n<p>Dat kan zeker. Vraag aan de verantwoordelijke persoon binnen jouw gemeente of organisatie om jou de nodige toegangsrechten te geven om van jou een projectmoderator te maken. Je kunt dan zelf je project en tijdslijn opzetten en de nodige informatie (video, documenten, afbeeldingen, ) delen. Ook kan je dan zelf anderen op het platform uitnodigen, waardoor ze binnen jouw project ideen kunnen posten, of stemmen en reageren op bestaande ideen.</p>\\n<h2>Kan ik als vereniging/organisatie/comit deelnemen?</h2>\\n<p>Ja, dat kan. Omdat voor andere gebruikers van het platform enkel je voornaam en naam zichtbaar is, vul je binnen je profiel dus gewoon de naam van je vereniging in. Bvb. naam: <em>vzw</em> en voornaam: <em>De Globetrotters</em>. Ongeacht je e-mailadres, zien andere mensen enkel <em>vzw De Globetrotters</em>.</p>\\n<h2>Waarom zou ik dit platform gebruiken en niet zelf een website maken?</h2>\\n<p>Een team van gedreven developers en specialisten in online participatie (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, in opdracht van jouw gemeente of organisatie) is dagelijks bezig met dit platform te verbeteren en te updaten. De kleinste bug wordt direct aangepakt en als je zelf creatieve voorstellen hebt, kunnen we je zeggen welke toepassingen van het platform je hiervoor kunt gebruiken of welke er in de pijplijn zitten.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"4d291006-0414-4f93-903b-fb911a00d510\\" alt=\\"Horizontale scheidingsregel\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Meer informatie nodig? </em></strong><em>Wil je het platform gebruiken? Vragen of feedback? Contacteer de verantwoordelijke dienst of persoon van je gemeente of organisatie of neem contact met Go Vocal via <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a></em></p><strong></strong>", "pa-IN": "<p>This <strong>all-in-one participation platform</strong> is an initiative of your municipality or organisation and can be used for different public consultation processes: collecting ideas, voting, discussing, surveys, polls, participatory budgeting, online mapping, scenario planning, support for advisory boards and committees, ...</p>\\n<p>On the home page, you'll see which <strong>processes are active </strong>and in which <strong>phase </strong>they currently are.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>How do I sign in on the platform?</h2>\\n<p>Signing in is done easily by giving your first and last name and your e-mail address. You could also use your Google or Facebook account. Only your first and last name will be visible to others.</p>\\n<h2>Can I use the platform myself, e.g. to organise a public consultation?</h2>\\n<p>Absolutely. Ask the responsible within your municipality or organisation to give you the needed permission rights to become a project moderator. Once granted these permissions, you can set up your own project and timeline and share the information you want (video, documents, images, ...). This will also allow you to invite others to the platform, enabling them to post ideas within your project, vote or comment.</p>\\n<h2>Can I participate as an association/organisation/committee? </h2>\\n<p>Yes, that's possible. Given that only your first and last name are visible to others on the platform, you can simply use your organisation's name while setting up your profile.</p>\\n<h2>Why would I use this platform and not create a website myself?</h2>\\n<p>A team of dedicated developers and specialists in online participation (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, commissioned by your municipality or organisation) is improving and updating this platform on a daily basis. Even the smallest bug gets tackled immediately and if you have creative proposals, they can help you pointing out which features of the platform can be used for this or which ones are in the pipeline.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Need more information?</em></strong><em> Do you want to use the platform? Questions or feedback? Contact the responsible within your municipality or organisation. Or contact Go Vocal through <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "pl-PL": "<p>Ta <strong>platforma partycypacyjna</strong> jest inicjatyw Twojej gminy lub organizacji i moe by wykorzystana w rnych procesach konsultacji spoecznych: zbieranie pomysw, gosowania, dyskusji, przeprowadzania ankiet, przeprowadzania bada, gosowania nad budetem partycypacyjnym, mapowania online, planowania scenariuszy, wsparcie dla rad doradczych i komisji, ...</p>\\n<p>Na stronie gwnej zobaczysz, ktre <strong>procesy s aktywne </strong>i na jakim <strong>etapie</strong> s obecnie.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>Jak zalogowa si na platformie?</h2>\\n<p>Logowanie jest proste i moesz tego dokona przez podanie swojego imienia i nazwiska oraz adresu e-mail. Moesz rwnie uy swojego konta Google lub Facebook. Tylko Twoje imi i nazwisko bdzie widoczne dla innych.</p>\\n<h2>Czy mog samodzielnie korzysta z platformy, np. w celu zorganizowania konsultacji spoecznych?</h2>\\n<p>Oczywicie. Popro osob odpowiedzialn w Twojej gminie lub organizacji, aby nadaa Ci niezbdne uprawnienia do zostania moderatorem projektu. Po przyznaniu tych uprawnie, moesz stworzy wasny projekt i o czasu oraz dzieli si informacjami (video, dokumenty, zdjcia, ...). Pozwoli Ci to rwnie na zapraszanie innych do platformy, umoliwiajc im zamieszczanie pomysw w ramach Twojego projektu, gosowanie lub komentowanie.</p>\\n<h2>Czy mog uczestniczy jako stowarzyszenie/organizacja/komitet? </h2>\\n<p>Tak, jest to moliwe. Biorc pod uwag, e tylko Twoje imi i nazwisko s widoczne dla innych na platformie, moesz po prostu uy nazwy swojej organizacji podczas tworzenia swojego profilu.</p>\\n<h2>Dlaczego miabym korzysta z tej platformy, a nie tworzy stron internetow samemu?</h2>\\n<p>Zesp dedykowanych programistw i specjalistw ds. uczestnictwa online (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, na zlecenie Twojej gminy lub organizacji) codziennie ulepsza i aktualizuje t platform. Nawet najmniejszy bd jest rozwizywany natychmiast. Jeli masz kreatywne propozycje, zesp CitizeLab pomoe Ci wskaza, ktre funkcje platformy mog by wykorzystane w celu ich realizacji lub ktre funkcje s w przygotowaniu.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Potrzebujesz wicej informacji?</em></strong><em> Czy chcesz korzysta z platformy? Masz pytania lub uwagi? Skontaktuj si z osob odpowiedzialn w Twojej gminie lub organizacji. Moesz te skontaktowa si z Go Vocal poprzez <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "pt-BR": "<p>This <strong>all-in-one participation platform</strong> is an initiative of your municipality or organisation and can be used for different public consultation processes: collecting ideas, voting, discussing, surveys, polls, participatory budgeting, online mapping, scenario planning, support for advisory boards and committees, ...</p>\\n<p>On the home page, you'll see which <strong>processes are active </strong>and in which <strong>phase </strong>they currently are.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>How do I sign in on the platform?</h2>\\n<p>Signing in is done easily by giving your first and last name and your e-mail address. You could also use your Google or Facebook account. Only your first and last name will be visible to others.</p>\\n<h2>Can I use the platform myself, e.g. to organise a public consultation?</h2>\\n<p>Absolutely. Ask the responsible within your municipality or organisation to give you the needed permission rights to become a project moderator. Once granted these permissions, you can set up your own project and timeline and share the information you want (video, documents, images, ...). This will also allow you to invite others to the platform, enabling them to post ideas within your project, vote or comment.</p>\\n<h2>Can I participate as an association/organisation/committee? </h2>\\n<p>Yes, that's possible. Given that only your first and last name are visible to others on the platform, you can simply use your organisation's name while setting up your profile.</p>\\n<h2>Why would I use this platform and not create a website myself?</h2>\\n<p>A team of dedicated developers and specialists in online participation (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, commissioned by your municipality or organisation) is improving and updating this platform on a daily basis. Even the smallest bug gets tackled immediately and if you have creative proposals, they can help you pointing out which features of the platform can be used for this or which ones are in the pipeline.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Need more information?</em></strong><em> Do you want to use the platform? Questions or feedback? Contact the responsible within your municipality or organisation. Or contact Go Vocal through <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "ro-RO": "<p> Aceast <strong> platform de participare integral </strong> este o iniiativ a oraului sau organizaiei dvs. i poate fi utilizat pentru diferite procese de consultare public: colectare de idei, votare, discuii, chestionare, sondaje, bugetare participativ, cartografiere online, planificare de scenarii, sprijin pentru consilii consultative i comisii, ... </p>\\n<p> Pe pagina principal, vei vedea care sunt <strong> procesele active </strong> i n ce faz se afl n prezent. </p>\\n<p> <img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Regula de separare orizontal\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"> </p>\\n<h2> Cum m conectez pe platform? </h2>\\n<p> Conectarea se face cu uurin, dndu-v numele, prenumele i adresa de e-mail. De asemenea, putei utiliza contul Google sau Facebook. Numai numele i prenumele dvs. vor fi vizibile pentru ceilali. </p>\\n<h2> Pot folosi platforma, pentru a organiza o consultare public? </h2>\\n<p> Absolut. Rugai responsabilii din oraul sau organizaia dvs. s v acorde drepturile de permisiune necesare pentru a deveni un moderator de proiect. Odat ce ai primit aceste permisiuni, putei configura propriul proiect i propria cronologie i putei distribui informaiile dorite (video, documente, imagini, ...). Acest lucru v va permite, de asemenea, s invitai altepersoane pe platform, permindu-le s posteze idei n cadrul proiectului, s voteze sau s comenteze. </p>\\n<h2> Pot participa ca asociaie / organizaie / comitet? </h2>\\n<p> Da, este posibil. Avnd n vedere c doar prenumele i prenumele dvs. sunt vizibile pentru ceilali de pe platform, putei utiliza pur i simplu numele organizaiei dvs. n timpul configurarii profilului. </p>\\n<h2> De ce a folosi aceast platform i nu a crea singur un site web? </h2>\\n<p> O echip de dezvoltatori dedicai i specialiti n participarea online (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\"> Go Vocal, </a> comandat de municipalitatea sau organizaia dvs.) mbuntete i actualizeaz zilnic aceast platform. Chiar i cea mai mic eroare este tratat imediat i dac avei propuneri creative, platforma v pot ajuta s evideniai care sunt caracteristicile care pot fi utilizate pentru aceasta. </p>\\n<p> <img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Regula de separare orizontal\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"> </p>\\n<p> Marea <em> Ai nevoie de mai multe informaii? </em> <em> Vrei s foloseti platforma? Ai ntrebri sau preri? Contactai responsabilii din cadrul municipalitii sau organizaiei dvs. sau contactai Go Vocal prin <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>. </em> </p>", "sr-SP": "<p>This <strong>all-in-one participation platform</strong> is an initiative of your municipality or organisation and can be used for different public consultation processes: collecting ideas, voting, discussing, surveys, polls, participatory budgeting, online mapping, scenario planning, support for advisory boards and committees, ...</p>\\n<p>On the home page, you'll see which <strong>processes are active </strong>and in which <strong>phase </strong>they currently are.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>How do I sign in on the platform?</h2>\\n<p>Signing in is done easily by giving your first and last name and your e-mail address. You could also use your Google or Facebook account. Only your first and last name will be visible to others.</p>\\n<h2>Can I use the platform myself, e.g. to organise a public consultation?</h2>\\n<p>Absolutely. Ask the responsible within your municipality or organisation to give you the needed permission rights to become a project moderator. Once granted these permissions, you can set up your own project and timeline and share the information you want (video, documents, images, ...). This will also allow you to invite others to the platform, enabling them to post ideas within your project, vote or comment.</p>\\n<h2>Can I participate as an association/organisation/committee? </h2>\\n<p>Yes, that's possible. Given that only your first and last name are visible to others on the platform, you can simply use your organisation's name while setting up your profile.</p>\\n<h2>Why would I use this platform and not create a website myself?</h2>\\n<p>A team of dedicated developers and specialists in online participation (<a href=\\"https://www.govocal.com/en\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Go Vocal</a>, commissioned by your municipality or organisation) is improving and updating this platform on a daily basis. Even the smallest bug gets tackled immediately and if you have creative proposals, they can help you pointing out which features of the platform can be used for this or which ones are in the pipeline.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"392d0e47-e5f9-41ab-9ceb-affac617b8b1\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<p><strong><em>Need more information?</em></strong><em> Do you want to use the platform? Questions or feedback? Contact the responsible within your municipality or organisation. Or contact Go Vocal through <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>.</em></p><strong></strong>", "sv-SE": "<p>Den hr <strong>helhetslsningen till plattform fr deltagande</strong> r ett initiativ frn din kommun eller organisation och kan anvndas fr olika offentliga samrdsprocesser: samla in ider, rsta, diskutera, underskningar, omrstningar, deltagande budgetering, onlinekartlggning, scenarieplanering, std fr rdgivande nmnder och kommitter, ...</p>\\n<p>P startsidan ser du vilka <strong>processer som r aktiva </strong>och i vilken <strong>fas </strong>de finns fr nrvarande.</p>\\n<p><img data-cl2-text-image-text-reference=\\"e2c7bc7a-017d-4887-a3cb-b94185617a59\\" alt=\\"Horizontal separation rule\\" data-align=\\"center\\" style=\\"display:block;margin:auto;\\"></p>\\n<h2>Hur loggar jag in p plattformen?</h2>\\n<p>Du loggar enkelt in genom att ange ditt fr- och efternamn samt din e-postadress. Du kan ocks anvnda ditt Google- eller Facebook-konto. Endast ditt fr- och efternamn kommer att visas fr andra.</p>\\n<h2>Kan jag anvnda plattformen sjlv, t.ex. fr att organisera ett offentligt samrd?</h2>\\n<p>Absolut. Be den ansvariga i din kommun eller organisation att ge dig ndvndiga behrigheter fr att bli projektmoderator. Nr du har bev