on: //insert client contacts</p> <h2>1. PRIVACY POLICY</h2> <p>This Privacy Policy applies to the Personal Data collected by Go Vocal on behalf of the organization through this website.</p> <h2>2. WHAT ARE PERSONAL DATA?</h2> <p>In this Privacy Policy, Personal Data refers to information that makes it possible to identify you. An identifiable person is someone who can be identified, either directly or indirectly, in particular by referring to an identification number or to one or more factors that are linked to physical, physiological, mental, economic, cultural or social identity. A typical example of personal information is your name and email address.</p> <h2>3. WHAT PERSONAL DATA DO WE COLLECT?</h2> <p>We might collect your Personal Data from the following three sources:</p> <h3>3.1 Personal Data that you provide during the registration process on the Platform, some of which are optional.</h3> <p>The personal data that we might collect from you are:</p> <ul> <li>First and last name</li> <li>E-mail address</li> <li>Year of birth</li> <li>Gender</li> <li>Area of residence</li> <li>Preferred language</li> </ul> <p>This list can be extended on request of the organization. If you choose to sign-in via a 3rd party authentication provider as Google Accounts, Facebook or FranceConnect, we will get this data from them. If you choose to verify your identity with a 3rd party identity provider as COW, FranceConnect or CSAM, we will get this information from them.</p> <h3>3.2 Personal data that you provide when taking participative action on our platform.</h3> <p>Every action you take on the platform (voting, posting an idea, writing a comment, answering a poll,) is registered and stored. This data is also linked to your registration data (3.1), implying that the organization can link your platform profile to this participation data.</p> <h3>3.3 Personal Data that we collect when you visit our platform.</h3> <p>We (and third party processors acting on our behalf) collect information about usage of our platform for assessing the good functioning and security of the platform. To this end, we collect technical information that can identify you, such as your IP address and browser details. By using our services you agree to this data being collected.</p> <p>We also gather usage data to improve our services, you can opt-out of this collection at all time from the consent manager.</p> <h2>4. HOW DO WE USE PERSONAL DATA?</h2> <p>We might use your personal data for the following purposes:</p> <ul> <li>First and foremost, to communicate your input to the organization with relevant context, and to draw aggregated reports of all the data collected on this platform to assist their decision-making.</li> <li>To create and maintain your user profile on this website.</li> <li>To manage the identification and authentication of users.</li> <li>To provide information about your community and/or alert you when activities on the platform may interest you. You can opt-out of user emails from your user profile at any time.</li> <li>To improve our services and monitor their functionalities.</li> </ul> <p>The personal data is only stored and processed for the period required for the purpose of the processing. After that, the data will be deleted or anonymized.</p> <h2>5. WITH WHOM DO WE SHARE YOUR PERSONAL DATA?</h2> <p>We share your personal data with the organization on behalf of which we gather this data. We share your data to the sub-processors working on our behalf. We will never sell or rent your personal data to other service providers, nor will we share your Personal Data with any service providers who are not compliant with the GDPR.</p> <h2>6. WHERE DO WE TRANSFER YOUR PERSONAL DATA TO?</h2> <p>We only transfer your Personal Data to service providers established outside the European Economic Area if they comply to art 44 GDPR.</p> <h2>7. WHAT RIGHTS DO YOU HAVE?</h2> <p>You have the right to view your personal data at any time, as well as the right to be informed of the use that Go Vocal makes of your personal data.</p> <h3>7.1 Right to rectification, erasure and restriction of processing</h3> <p>You are free to decide whether or not to provide your personal data to Go Vocal. In addition, you always have the right to request Go Vocal to correct, supplement or remove your personal data. You acknowledge that a refusal to provide or a request for the erasure of personal data means that certain services can no longer be delivered. You may also request that the processing of your personal data is limited. If you choose to remove your account from the platform, the personal data that was collected about you will be removed from our servers. Some personal information about you might remain in the logging data we keep for security and legal reasons for up to 30 days.</p> <h3>7.2 Right to object</h3> <p>You have the right to object to the processing of your personal data for serious and legitimate reasons. In addition, you always have the right to object to the use of your personal data for direct marketing purposes; in such cases, you do not have to state reasons.</p> <h3>7.3 Right to data portability</h3> <p>You have the right to obtain the personal data you have provided to Go Vocal in a structured, typical and machine-readable form and/or have such transferred to different controllers.</p> <h3>7.4 Right to withdraw consent</h3> <p>Insofar as the processing is based on your prior consent, you have the right to withdraw this approval.</p> <h3>7.5 Exercising your rights</h3> <p>You can exercise your rights by contacting Go Vocal to this end, either by email to <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>, by post to Pachecolaan 34, 1000 Brussels, Belgium or by using the Contact us form on our Website, provided you enclose a copy of the front of your identity card.</p> <h3>7.6 Automated decision-making and profiling</h3> <p>The processing of your personal data does not include profiling and shall also not be subjected by Go Vocal to automated decision-making.</p> <h3>7.7 Right to lodge a complaint</h3> <p>You have the right to lodge a complaint to the Privacy authority of your country, or the Belgian Privacy Authority under which authority Go Vocal falls: Drukpersstraat 35, 1000 Brussels, Belgium, Tel +32 (0)2 274 48 00, Fax +32 (0)2 274 48 35, e-mail: <a href=\\"mailto:contact@adp-gba.be\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">contact@adp-gba.be</a>. This does not affect relief before a civil court.</p> <h2>8. ADDITIONAL INFORMATION ON DATA COLLECTION AND PROCESSING</h2> <h3>Legal procedures</h3> <p>Go Vocal and the Organization we process this data for might use the Personal Data of the User for legal purposes, for the court or legal proceedings preceding phases in the event of unlawful use of this Application or the related services. The User is aware that Go Vocal and the Organization we work with might be obliged to disclose the personal data at the request of competent government institutions for the processing of the Data. The legal basis for this processing is the acceptance of the terms and conditions (contractual basis) and given consent.</p> <h3>Security Measures</h3> <p>Go Vocal has developed security measures which have been adjusted at the technological and organisational level to prevent the destruction, loss, falsification, changing, prohibited access or the erroneous disclosure to third parties of personal data as well as any other prohibited processing of this data. Under no circumstances can Go Vocal be held liable for any direct or indirect loss resulting from the incorrect or unlawful use of your personal data by a third party. You must at all times comply with the security instructions, including by preventing all prohibited access to your login details and password. You are solely responsible for the use made from the website on your computer, IP-address and your identification details, as well as for the confidentiality of such.</p> <h3>Changes to this privacy policy</h3> <p>Go Vocal reserves the right to change this privacy policy at any time by notifying Users on this page. We encourage you to check this page for possible changes. The date of the last change is indicated at the bottom of the page. If a User objects to any change in the policy, the User must not continue to use this Application. Unless otherwise indicated, the valid Privacy Policy applicable at that time applies to all Personal Data that we have collected.</p> <p><em>Most recent update: 17/12/2019</em></p>\\n", "sr-Latn": "<p> Odgovorni za obradu podataka: </p> <p> Go Vocal NV - Pachecolaan 34 - 1000 Brisel - Belgija </p> <p> Email adresa za kontakt: <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a> </p> <p> Organizacija: // ubacite kontakt klijenta </p> <h2> 1. POLITIKA PRIVATNOSTI </h2> <p> Ova Politika privatnosti odnosi se na Line podatke koje je Go Vocal prikupio u ime organizacije putem ove web stranice. </p> <h2> 2. TA SU LINI PODACI? </h2> <p> U ovoj politici privatnosti lini podaci se odnose na informacije koje omogucuju vau identifikaciju. Lice koje je moguce identifikovati je neko ko se moe identifikovati, bilo direktno ili indirektno, posebnim pozivanjem na identifikacioni broj ili na jedan ili vie faktora koji su povezani sa fizikim, fiziolokim, mentalnim, ekonomskim, kulturnim ili socijalnim identitetom. Tipian primer linih podataka su vae ime i email adresa. </p> <h2> 3. KOJE LINE PODATKE PRIKUPLJAMO? </h2> <p> Vae line podatke moemo prikupiti iz sledeca tri izvora: </p> <h3> 3.1 lini podaci koje navedete tokom postupka registracije na platformi, od kojih neki nisu obavezni. </h3> <p> Lini podaci koje bismo mogli prikupiti od vas su: </p> <ul> <li> Ime i prezime </li> <li> Email adresa </li> <li> Godina roenja </li> <li> Pol </li> <li> Mesto prebivalita </li> <li> eljeni jezik </li> </ul> <p> Ovu listu moete proiriti na zahtev organizacije. Ako se odluite da se prijavite preko nezavisnog identiteta poput Google naloga, Facebook-a ili FranceConnect, od njih cemo dobiti ove podatke. Ako odluite da verifikujete svoj identitet kod nezavisnog provajdera identifikacije kao COV, FranceConnect ili CSAM, od njih cemo dobiti ove informacije. </p> <h3> 3.2 Lini podaci koje navedete prilikom preduzimanja participativnih radnji na naoj platformi. &lt; / h3&gt; </h3><p> Svaka akcija koju preduzmete na platformi (glasanje, objavljivanje ideje, pisanje komentara, odgovaranje na anketu, ...) se registruje i uva. Ovi podaci su takoe povezani sa vaim podacima o registraciji (3.1), to podrazumeva da organizacija moe povezati va profil na platformi sa ovim podacima o uecu. </p> <h3> 3.3 Lini podaci koje prikupljamo kada posetite nau platformu. </h3> <p> Mi (i nezavisni procesori koji deluju u nae ime) prikupljamo informacije o koricenju nae platforme za procenu dobrog funkcionisanja i sigurnosti platforme. U tu svrhu prikupljamo tehnike informacije koje vas mogu identifikovati, kao to su vaa IP adresa i detalji pretraivaa. Koricenjem naih usluga pristajete da se ovi podaci prikupljaju. </p> <p> Takoe prikupljamo podatke o koricenju kako bismo poboljali nae usluge. Uvek moete da onemogucite ovo putem menadera saglasnosti. </p> &lt; h2&gt; 4. KAKO KORISTIMO LINE PODATKE?  <p> Vae line podatke moemo koristiti u sledece svrhe: </p> <ul> <li> Prvo i najvanije, da bismo vae podatke preneli organizaciji sa relevantnim kontekstom, kako bi kreirala objedinjene izvetaje o svim podacima prikupljenim na ovoj platformi i imala pomo prilikom donoenja odluka. </li> <li> U svrhe kreiranja i odravanja vaeg korisnikog profila na ovoj web lokaciji. </li> <li> Za upravljanje identifikacijom i potvrdom identiteta korisnika. </li> <li> Da bismo vam pruili informacije o zajednici i/ili vas obavestili u sluaju kada bi vas aktivnosti na platformi mogle zanimati. U svakom trenutku moete da onemogucite email obavetenja putem svog korisnikog profila. </li> <li> Da biste poboljali nae usluge i nadzirali njihove funkcionalnosti. </li> </ul> <p> Lini podaci se uvaju za period potreban radi obrade. Nakon toga, podaci ce biti izbrisani ili anonimizirani. </p> <h2> 5. SA KIM DELIMO VAE LINE PODATKE? </h2> <p> Vae line podatke delimo sa organizacijom u ime koje prikupljamo ove podatke. Vae podatke delimo sa potprocesorima koji rade u nae ime. Nikada necemo prodati ili iznajmiti vae line podatke drugim dobavljaima usluga, niti cemo deliti vae line podatke sa bilo kojim dobavljaem usluga koji nije u skladu sa GDPR-om. </p> <h2> 6. GDE PRENOSIMO VAE LINE PODATKE? </h2> <p> Vae line podatke prenosimo samo dobavljaima usluga sa seditem van Evropskog ekonomskog prostora ako su u skladu sa lanom 44 GDPR.</p><h2> 7. KOJA PRAVA IMATE? </h2> <p> Imate pravo da pregledate svoje line podatke u bilo kom trenutku, kao i pravo da budete obaveteni o upotrebi vaih linih podataka od strane Go Vocal-a. </p> &lt; h3&gt; 7.1 Pravo na ispravku, brisanje i ogranienje obrade  <p> Slobodni ste da odluite da li cete svoje line podatke dostaviti Go Vocalu ili ne. Pored toga, uvek imate pravo da zatraite da Go Vocal ispravi, dopuni ili ukloni vae line podatke. Pristajete da odbijanje pruanja ili zahtev za brisanje linih podataka znai da odreene usluge vie ne mogu biti isporuene. Takoe moete zatraiti da obrada vaih linih podataka bude ograniena. Ako odluite da uklonite svoj nalog sa platforme, lini podaci prikupljeni o vama bice uklonjeni sa naih servera. Neki lini podaci o vama mogli bi ostati u evidencijskim podacima koje uvamo iz sigurnosnih i pravnih razloga do 30 dana. </p> <h3> 7.2 Pravo na prigovor </h3> <p> Imate pravo da uloite prigovor na obradu vaih linih podataka iz ozbiljnih i legitimnih razloga. Pored toga, uvek imate pravo da prigovorite upotrebi svojih linih podataka u svrhe direktnog marketinga; u takvim sluajevima ne morate da navodite razloge. </p> <h3> 7.3 Pravo na prenosivost podataka </h3> <p> Imate pravo da line podatke koje ste dostavili Go Vocalu pribavite u struktuiranom, tipinom obliku i mainski itljivom obrascu i/ili da takve prenesete razliitim kontrolorima. </p> <h3> 7.4 Pravo na povlaenje saglasnosti </h3> <p> Ukoliko se obrada zasniva na vaoj prethodnoj saglasnosti, imate pravo da povuete ovo odobrenje. </p> <h3> 7.5 Ostvarivanje linih prava </h3> <p> Svoja prava moete ostvariti tako to ete kontaktirati Go Vocal, putem email-a na <a href=\\"mailto:support@govocal.com\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">support@govocal.com</a>, ili potom na Pachecolaan 34, 1000 Brisel, Belgija, ili pomocu obrasca Kontaktirajte nas na naoj veb lokaciji, pod uslovom da priloite kopiju prednje strane svoje line karte. </p> <h3> 7.6 Automatsko donoenje odluka i profilisanje </h3> <p> Obrada vaih linih podataka ne ukljuuje profilisanje i Go Vocal ih takoe nece podvrgavati automatskom donoenju odluka. </p> <h3> 7.7 Pravo na ulaganje albe </h3> <p> Imate Pravo podnoenja albe organu za zatitu privatnosti vae zemlje ili belgijskom organu za zatitu privatnosti pod kojim je Go Vocal nadlean: Drukpersstraat 35, 1000 Brisel, Belgija, Tel +32 (0) 2 274 48 00, faks +32 (0 ) 2 274 48 35, e-mail: <a href=\\"mailto:contact@adp-gba.be\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\\">contact@adp-gba.be</a>. To ne utie na olakanje pred graanskim sudom. </p> <h2> 8. DODATNE INFORMACIJE O PRIKUPLJANJU I OBRADI PODATAKA </h2> <h3> Pravni postupci </h3> <p> Go Vocal i Organizacije kojima obraujemo ove podatke mogu koristiti Line podatke Korisnika u pravne svrhe, za sudske ili pravne postupke prethodne faze u sluaju nezakonite upotrebe ove Aplikacije ili srodnih usluga. Korisnik je svestan da ce Go Vocal i Organizacija sa kojom radimo moda biti obavezni da otkriju line podatke na zahtev nadlenih dravnih institucija za obradu podataka. Pravni osnov za ovu obradu je prihvatanje uslova i odredbi (ugovorna osnova) i data saglasnost. </p> <h3> Mere bezbednosti </h3> <p> Go Vocal je razvio mere bezbednosti koje su tehnoloki prilagoene i organizacioni nivo za spreavanje unitavanja, gubitka, falsifikovanja, promene, zabranjenog pristupa ili pogrenog otkrivanja linih podataka trecim licima, kao i bilo koje druge zabranjene obrade ovih podataka. Go Vocal ni pod kojim okolnostima ne moe biti odgovoran za bilo kakav direktan ili indirektan gubitak koji je rezultat netane ili nezakonite upotrebe vaih linih podataka od strane trece strane. U svakom trenutku morate da se pridravate sigurnosnih uputstava, ukljuujuci spreavanje svih zabranjenih pristupa vaim detaljima za prijavu i lozinci. Sami ste odgovorni za upotrebu  na vaem raunaru, za IP adresu i vae identifikacione detalje, kao i za njihovu poverljivost. </p> <h3> Izmene ove politike privatnosti </h3> <p> Go Vocal zadrava pravo da u bilo kom trenutku promeni ovu politiku privatnosti tako to ce obavestiti korisnike na ovoj stranici. Savetujemo vam da na ovoj stranici pogledate moguce promene. Datum poslednje promene naveden je na dnu stranice. Ako se korisnik protivi nekoj promeni politike, korisnik ne sme da nastavi da koristi ovu aplikaciju. Ako nije drugaije naznaeno, vaeca Politika privatnosti koja se primenjuje u to vreme primenjuje se na sve line podatke koje smo prikupili. </p> <p> <em> Najnovije auriranje: 17.12.2019 </em> </p>\\n"}	f	full_width_banner_layout	\N	\N	{}	no_button	\N	{}	{}	t	f	f	no_filter	f	f	{}	\N
