 je van het platform ontvangt in je Instellingen. Daar is een rubriek \\"Meldingen\\" waar je e-mail-notificaties aan en uit kunt zetten.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Hoe verwijder ik mijn account?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">In je Instellingen is er de mogelijkheid om je account te verwijderen. Bijdragen die hebt geplaatst blijven zichtbaar, maar je naam wordt uit het bericht verwijderd en vervangen door 'onbekende auteur'. Als je al je bijdragen wilt verwijderen, doe dat dan voor je je account verwijdert.</p>", "pa-IN": "<h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What is this platform for?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">This platform is designed as a central hub to share information and get input and feedback. Participation projects that are currently active are shown on the homepage - each participation project may have a different mode of engagement, whether its adding an idea, commenting on a proposal, voting on and prioritising projects, or taking a survey.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I participate?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">You can always browse public projects, but youll need to sign up in order to take an action. This helps to maintain a community feel and ensure the legitimacy of the input.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What information can people see about me?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Your name, photo and bio, if youve added one, are visible. You can always change these in your Settings.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Why cant I post my input or submit a comment?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Posting, commenting and voting may be enabled only during certain times or phases of a project. In some instances, a project may only be open to contributions from a certain stakeholder group.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">If posting is currently enabled for a project, youll see a button that prompts you to submit a post. Alternatively, you can browse other active projects for additional engagement opportunities.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I edit or delete my input?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">If youve posted your input but want to make edits or delete it, you can find this option by clicking on the three small dots on the top right of the post.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What are the community guidelines and moderation policies?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Our community guidelines are here to help ensure that the platform is a safe space for everyone to participate. Please ensure your posts are free of:</p><ul>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Personal attacks, insults, abusive or discriminatory comments</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Offensive language including profanity</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Marketing or advertising material</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Personal information about other individuals</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Copyrighted material such as images</li>\\n  </ul><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Any posts or comments that do not adhere to these guidelines may be edited or deleted, or in extreme instances, prevented from being posted. Please review our Terms &amp; Conditions for more information.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I report an offensive post?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Click on the three small dots on the top right corner of the post to report it. Please indicate the reason you are reporting the content - this will send a notification for the post to be reviewed.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Why am I having difficulty signing up or logging in?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">If youre unable to sign up, it may be because youve already registered with the same email address or previously received an invitation to join the platform. If you see a message that your email address is taken by a pending invite, please check your email and follow the link in the invitation to register your account. If you cant find the invite, try looking in your spam box or request a new invitation.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I reset my password?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">You can always request to reset your password from the log in page. If you reset your password, a link will be sent to your email address - follow the instructions to change your password. For security reasons, the link is valid for one hour. If the link has expired, you can simply click on Forgot password? in the log in page again to generate a new reset link.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">If you didnt receive the email, check to make sure that its not in your spam and that youre sending the link to the same email address that you signed up with.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What will you do with my data?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Review our privacy policy for more information on data collection and usage. In short, we will never use your data for advertising, marketing or other types of spam.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What emails will I receive?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">You may receive emails related to your account and your activity on the platform, for instance, when someone responds to one of your posts. You can control which emails you receive in your Settings. There is a section called Notifications where you can turn email notifications on and off.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I delete my account?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">In your Settings there is the option to delete your account. Input that youve posted will remain published, but your name will be removed from the post and replaced with unknown author. If youd like to delete all of your input, please do so before deleting your account.</p>", "pl-PL": "<h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Do czego suy ta platforma?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Platforma ta zostaa zaprojektowana jako centralne miejsce wymiany informacji oraz pozyskiwania wkadu i opinii. Na stronie gwnej widoczne s aktualnie aktywne projekty partycypacyjne - kady projekt moe mie inny tryb zaangaowania, czy to poprzez dodanie pomysu, skomentowanie propozycji, gosowanie i ustalanie priorytetw projektw, czy te wypenienie ankiety.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Jak mog wzi udzia?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Zawsze moesz przeglda projekty publiczne, ale aby podj dziaanie, musisz si zarejestrowa. Pomaga to w utrzymaniu poczucia wsplnoty i zapewnia legalno wkadu, na przykad po to, by jedna osoba nie gosowaa wiele razy.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Jakie informacje o mnie mog zobaczy inni?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Twoje imi i nazwisko, zdjcie i bio, jeli je dodae, s widoczne. Zawsze moesz je zmieni w swoich Ustawieniach (link do: /profile/edit).</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Dlaczego nie mog wysa swojego wkadu lub komentarza?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Dodawanie postw, komentowanie i gosowanie moe by moliwe tylko w okrelonym czasie lub na okrelonych etapach projektu. W niektrych przypadkach, projekt moe by otwarty tylko dla wkadu od okrelonej grupy interesariuszy.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Jeli wysyanie postw jest obecnie wczone dla danego projektu, zobaczysz przycisk, ktry poprosi Ci o wysanie postu. Moesz te przejrze inne aktywne projekty, aby znale dodatkowe moliwoci zaangaowania.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Jak mog edytowa lub usun swj wkad?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Jeli wysae swj post, ale chcesz go edytowa lub usun, moesz znale t opcj klikajc na trzy mae kropki w prawym grnym rogu postu.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Jakie s wytyczne dla spoecznoci i zasady moderacji?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Nasze wytyczne dla spoecznoci maj na celu zapewnienie, e platforma jest bezpieczn przestrzeni dla kadego. Upewnij si, e Twoje posty s wolne od:</p><ul>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Atakw osobistych, obelg, obraliwych lub dyskryminujcych komentarzy</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Obraliwego jzyka, w tym blunierstw</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Materiaw marketingowych lub reklamowych</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Informacji osobistych o innych osobach</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Materiaw chronionych prawem autorskim, takich jak zdjcia.</li>\\n    </ul><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Wszelkie posty lub komentarze, ktre nie s zgodne z tymi wytycznymi, mog by edytowane lub usuwane, a w skrajnych przypadkach mog zosta zablokowane. Prosimy o zapoznanie si z naszymi Warunkami i Postanowieniami (link: /pages/terms-and-conditions), aby uzyska wicej informacji.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Jak mog zgosi obraliwy post?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Kliknij na trzy mae kropki w prawym grnym rogu postu, aby go zgosi. Podaj powd, dla ktrego zgaszasz tre - to spowoduje wysanie powiadomienia, aby post zosta przejrzany.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Dlaczego mam trudnoci z zarejestrowaniem si lub zalogowaniem?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Jeli nie moesz si zarejestrowa, moe to by spowodowane tym, e zarejestrowae si ju na ten sam adres e-mail lub wczeniej otrzymae zaproszenie do przyczenia si do platformy. Jeli zobaczysz komunikat, e Twj adres e-mail jest zajty przez oczekujce zaproszenie, sprawd swj e-mail i skorzystaj z linku w zaproszeniu, aby zarejestrowa swoje konto. Jeli nie moesz znale zaproszenia, sprbuj poszuka go w skrzynce spamowej lub popro o nowe zaproszenie.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Jak mog zresetowa swoje haso?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Zawsze moesz poprosi o zresetowanie swojego hasa na stronie logowania. Jeli zresetujesz swoje haso, na Twj adres e-mail zostanie wysany link - postpuj zgodnie z instrukcjami, aby zmieni swoje haso. Ze wzgldw bezpieczestwa link jest wany przez jedn godzin. Jeli link straci wano, moesz po prostu klikn na \\"Zapomniae hasa?\\" na stronie logowania, aby wygenerowa nowy link resetujcy.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Jeli nie otrzymae e-maila, sprawd, czy nie znajduje si on w spamie i czy wysyasz link na ten sam adres e-mail, na ktry si zarejestrowae.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Co zrobicie z moimi danymi?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Zapoznaj si z nasz polityk prywatnoci (link do: /pages/privacy-policy), aby uzyska wicej informacji na temat zbierania i wykorzystywania danych. W skrcie, nigdy nie bdziemy wykorzystywa Twoich danych do celw reklamowych, marketingowych lub innego rodzaju spamu.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Jakie e-maile bd otrzymywa?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Moesz otrzymywa wiadomoci e-mail zwizane z Twoim kontem i Twoj aktywnoci na platformie, na przykad, gdy kto odpowie na jeden z Twoich postw. Moesz kontrolowa, ktre e-maile otrzymujesz w swoich Ustawieniach (link do: /profile/edit). Znajduje si tam sekcja \\"Powiadomienia\\", gdzie moesz wczy lub wyczy powiadomienia e-mail.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Jak mog usun swoje konto?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">W ustawieniach (link do: /profile/edit) jest opcja usunicia konta. Wpisy, ktre opublikowae pozostan opublikowane, ale twoje imi zostanie usunite z postu i zastpione sowami \\"anonimowy autor\\". Jeli chciaby usun wszystkie swoje wpisy, zrb to przed usuniciem konta. </p>", "pt-BR": "<h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Para que serve esta plataforma?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Esta plataforma  projetada como um ncleo central para compartilhar, receber informaes e feedbacks. Os projetos de participao atualmente ativos so mostrados na pgina inicial - cada projeto de participao pode ter um modo diferente de engajamento, seja adicionando uma ideia, comentando uma proposta, votando e priorizando projetos, ou fazendo uma pesquisa.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Como posso participar?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Voc sempre pode navegar pelos projetos pblicos, mas precisar se inscrever para poder realizar uma ao. Isto ajuda a manter a relao de comunidade e garantir transparncia sobre a contribuio.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Que informaes as pessoas podem ver sobre mim?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Seu nome, foto e biografia, se voc adicionou uma, so visveis. Voc sempre pode mud-los em suas Configuraes.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Por que eu no posso postar minhas informaes ou enviar um comentrio?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Postar, comentar e votar pode ser habilitado somente durante certos momentos ou fases de um projeto. Em alguns casos, um projeto pode estar aberto apenas a contribuies de um determinado grupo de interessados.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Quando a postagem estiver habilitada para um projeto, voc ver um boto que permite que voc envie uma postagem. Alternativamente, voc pode navegar por outros projetos ativos para oportunidades adicionais de engajamento.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Como posso editar ou apagar minhas contribuies?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Se voc publicou seu comentrio mas deseja fazer edies ou exclu-lo, voc pode encontrar esta opo clicando nos trs pequenos pontos na parte superior  direita da postagem.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Quais so as diretrizes da comunidade e as polticas de moderao?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Nossas diretrizes da comunidade esto aqui para ajudar a garantir que a plataforma seja um espao seguro para que todos possam participar. Por favor, certifique-se de que suas postagens estejam livres de:</p><ul>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Ataques pessoais, insultos, comentrios abusivos ou discriminatrios</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Linguagem ofensiva incluindo profanidade</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Material de marketing ou publicidade</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Informaes pessoais sobre outras pessoas</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Material protegido por direitos autorais, como imagens</li>\\n    </ul><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Quaisquer postagens ou comentrios que no cumpram estas diretrizes podem ser editados ou excludos, ou em casos extremos, impedidos de serem postados. Favor rever nossos Termos e Condies para maiores informaes.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Como posso relatar um post ofensivo?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Clique nos trs pequenos pontos na parte superior direita do post para relatar. Favor indicar o motivo pelo qual voc est notificando sobre o contedo - isto enviar uma notificao para que o post seja revisado.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Por que estou tendo dificuldade para me inscrever ou entrar no sistema?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Se voc no conseguir se inscrever, pode ser porque voc j se inscreveu com o mesmo endereo de e-mail ou recebeu anteriormente um convite para se inscrever na plataforma. Se voc vir uma mensagem de que seu endereo de e-mail tem um convite pendente, verifique seu e-mail e siga o link no convite para registrar sua conta. Se voc no conseguir encontrar o convite, tente procurar em sua caixa de spam ou solicitar um novo convite.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Como fao para redefinir minha senha?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Voc pode sempre solicitar a redefinio de sua senha a partir da pgina de login. Se voc redefinir sua senha, um link ser enviado para seu endereo de e-mail - siga as instrues para alterar sua senha. Por razes de segurana, o link  vlido por uma hora. Se o link tiver expirado, voc pode simplesmente clicar em 'Esqueceu sua senha?' na pgina de login novamente para gerar um novo link de redefinio.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Se voc no recebeu o e-mail, verifique se ele no est em seu spam e se voc est enviando o link para o mesmo endereo de e-mail com o qual voc se inscreveu.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">O que vocs fazem com meus dados?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Revise nossa poltica de privacidade para obter mais informaes sobre coleta e uso de dados. Em resumo, nunca utilizaremos seus dados para publicidade, marketing ou outros tipos de spam.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Quais e-mails eu receberei?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Voc poder receber e-mails relacionados  sua conta e  sua atividade na plataforma, por exemplo, quando algum responder a uma de suas postagens. Voc pode controlar quais e-mails voc recebe em suas configuraes. H uma seo chamada \\"Notificaes\\" onde voc pode ativar e desativar as notificaes de e-mail.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Como fao para excluir minha conta?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Em suas configuraes h a opo de apagar sua conta. As postagens permanecero publicadas, mas seu nome ser removido do post e substitudo por \\"autor desconhecido\\". Se voc quiser excluir todas as suas postagens faa-o, por gentileza, antes de excluir sua conta.</p>", "ro-RO": "<h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Pentru ce este aceast platform?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Aceast platform este conceput ca un punct central pentru a face schimb de informaii i pentru a obine contribuii i feedback. Proiectele de participare care sunt active n prezent sunt afiate pe pagina de pornire - fiecare proiect de participare poate avea un mod diferit de implicare, fie c este vorba de adugarea unei idei, comentarea unei propuneri, votarea i prioritizarea proiectelor sau participarea la un sondaj.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Cum pot participa?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Putei oricnd s rsfoii proiectele publice, dar va trebui s v nscriei pentru a ntreprinde o aciune. Acest lucru ajut la meninerea unui sentiment de comunitate i asigur legitimitatea contribuiilor.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Ce informaii pot vedea oamenii despre mine?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Numele, fotografia i biografia dumneavoastr, dac ai adugat una, sunt vizibile. Putei oricnd s le modificai n Setri.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">De ce nu pot s mi postez contribuia sau s trimit un comentariu?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Postarea, comentariile i votul pot fi activate doar n anumite momente sau faze ale unui proiect. n unele cazuri, un proiect poate fi deschis doar pentru contribuiile unui anumit grup de pri interesate.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Dac postarea este activat n prezent pentru un proiect, vei vedea un buton care v invit s trimitei o postare. Alternativ, putei naviga prin alte proiecte active pentru oportuniti suplimentare de implicare.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Cum mi editez sau terg datele introduse?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Dac v-ai publicat contribuia, dar dorii s o modificai sau s o tergei, putei gsi aceast opiune fcnd clic pe cele trei puncte mici din dreapta sus a postrii.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Care sunt liniile directoare ale comunitii i politicile de moderare?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Liniile noastre directoare ale comunitii sunt aici pentru a ne ajuta s ne asigurm c platforma este un spaiu sigur pentru ca toat lumea s participe. V rugm s v asigurai c postrile dvs. sunt lipsite de:</p><ul>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Atacuri personale, insulte, comentarii abuzive sau discriminatorii</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Limbaj ofensator, inclusiv blasfemii</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Materiale de marketing sau publicitate</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Materiale personale informaii despre alte persoane</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Materiale protejate de drepturi de autor, cum ar fi imagini</li>\\n    </ul><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Orice postri sau comentarii care nu respect aceste orientri pot fi editate sau terse, sau, n cazuri extreme, s nu poat fi postate. V rugm s consultai Termenii &amp; Condiiile pentru mai multe informaii.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Cum pot raporta o postare ofensatoare?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Facei clic pe cele trei puncte mici din colul din dreapta sus al mesajului pentru a-l raporta. V rugm s indicai motivul pentru care raportai coninutul - acest lucru va trimite o notificare pentru ca postarea s fie revizuit.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">De ce ntmpin dificulti la nscriere sau la conectare?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Dac nu reuii s v nscriei, este posibil s se datoreze faptului c v-ai nregistrat deja cu aceeai adres de e-mail sau ai primit anterior o invitaie de a v altura platformei. Dac vedei un mesaj care indic faptul c adresa dvs. de e-mail este ocupat de o invitaie n ateptare, v rugm s v verificai e-mailul i s urmai linkul din invitaie pentru a v nregistra contul. Dac nu gsii invitaia, ncercai s cutai n csua de spam sau solicitai o nou invitaie.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Cum mi resetez parola?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Putei oricnd s solicitai resetarea parolei din pagina de conectare. Dac v resetai parola, vi se va trimite un link la adresa dvs. de e-mail - urmai instruciunile pentru a v schimba parola. Din motive de securitate, linkul este valabil timp de o or. Dac linkul a expirat, putei face clic din nou pe \\"Forgot password?\\" (Ai uitat parola?) n pagina de conectare pentru a genera un nou link de resetare.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Dac nu ai primit e-mailul, verificai dac acesta nu se afl n spam i dac trimitei link-ul la aceeai adres de e-mail cu care v-ai nregistrat.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Ce vei face cu datele mele?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Consultai politica noastr de confidenialitate pentru mai multe informaii despre colectarea i utilizarea datelor. Pe scurt, nu vom folosi niciodat datele dvs. pentru publicitate, marketing sau alte tipuri de spam.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Ce e-mailuri voi primi?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Este posibil s primii e-mailuri legate de contul dvs. i de activitatea dvs. pe platform, de exemplu, atunci cnd cineva rspunde la una dintre postrile dvs. Putei controla ce e-mailuri primii n Setri. Exist o seciune numit \\"Notifications\\" (Notificri) n care putei activa i dezactiva notificrile prin e-mail.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Cum mi terg contul?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">n setrile dvs. exist opiunea de a v terge contul. Datele pe care le-ai postat vor rmne publicate, dar numele dvs. va fi eliminat din postare i va fi nlocuit cu \\"autor necunoscut\\". Dac dorii s tergei toate contribuiile dvs., v rugm s facei acest lucru nainte de a v terge contul.</p>", "sr-SP": "<h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What is this platform for?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">This platform is designed as a central hub to share information and get input and feedback. Participation projects that are currently active are shown on the homepage - each participation project may have a different mode of engagement, whether its adding an idea, commenting on a proposal, voting on and prioritising projects, or taking a survey.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I participate?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">You can always browse public projects, but youll need to sign up in order to take an action. This helps to maintain a community feel and ensure the legitimacy of the input.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What information can people see about me?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Your name, photo and bio, if youve added one, are visible. You can always change these in your Settings.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Why cant I post my input or submit a comment?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Posting, commenting and voting may be enabled only during certain times or phases of a project. In some instances, a project may only be open to contributions from a certain stakeholder group.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">If posting is currently enabled for a project, youll see a button that prompts you to submit a post. Alternatively, you can browse other active projects for additional engagement opportunities.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I edit or delete my input?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">If youve posted your input but want to make edits or delete it, you can find this option by clicking on the three small dots on the top right of the post.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What are the community guidelines and moderation policies?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Our community guidelines are here to help ensure that the platform is a safe space for everyone to participate. Please ensure your posts are free of:</p><ul>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Personal attacks, insults, abusive or discriminatory comments</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Offensive language including profanity</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Marketing or advertising material</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Personal information about other individuals</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Copyrighted material such as images</li>\\n  </ul><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Any posts or comments that do not adhere to these guidelines may be edited or deleted, or in extreme instances, prevented from being posted. Please review our Terms &amp; Conditions for more information.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I report an offensive post?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Click on the three small dots on the top right corner of the post to report it. Please indicate the reason you are reporting the content - this will send a notification for the post to be reviewed.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Why am I having difficulty signing up or logging in?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">If youre unable to sign up, it may be because youve already registered with the same email address or previously received an invitation to join the platform. If you see a message that your email address is taken by a pending invite, please check your email and follow the link in the invitation to register your account. If you cant find the invite, try looking in your spam box or request a new invitation.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I reset my password?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">You can always request to reset your password from the log in page. If you reset your password, a link will be sent to your email address - follow the instructions to change your password. For security reasons, the link is valid for one hour. If the link has expired, you can simply click on Forgot password? in the log in page again to generate a new reset link.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">If you didnt receive the email, check to make sure that its not in your spam and that youre sending the link to the same email address that you signed up with.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What will you do with my data?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Review our privacy policy for more information on data collection and usage. In short, we will never use your data for advertising, marketing or other types of spam.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What emails will I receive?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">You may receive emails related to your account and your activity on the platform, for instance, when someone responds to one of your posts. You can control which emails you receive in your Settings. There is a section called Notifications where you can turn email notifications on and off.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I delete my account?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">In your Settings there is the option to delete your account. Input that youve posted will remain published, but your name will be removed from the post and replaced with unknown author. If youd like to delete all of your input, please do so before deleting your account.</p>", "sv-SE": "<h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Vad r plattformen till fr?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Denna plattform r utformad som ett centralt nav fr att dela information och f input och feedback. Delaktighetsprojekt som fr nrvarande r aktiva visas p hemsidan - varje delaktighetsprojekt kan ha olika stt att engagera sig, oavsett om det handlar om att lgga till en id, kommentera ett frslag, rsta om och prioritera projekt eller delta i en enkt.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Hur deltar jag?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Du kan alltid blddra bland offentliga projekt, men du mste registrera dig fr att kunna vidta en tgrd. Detta bidrar till att bibehlla en gemenskapsknsla och skerstlla att bidragen r legitima.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Vilken information kan folk se om mig?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Ditt namn, foto och biografi, om du har lagt till en sdan, r synliga. Du kan alltid ndra dessa i dina instllningar.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Varfr kan jag inte lgga upp mitt inlgg eller lmna en kommentar?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Inlgg, kommentarer och omrstningar kan vara aktiverade endast under vissa tider eller faser av ett projekt. I vissa fall kan ett projekt endast vara ppet fr bidrag frn en viss intressentgrupp.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Om publicering fr nrvarande r aktiverat fr ett projekt visas en knapp som uppmanar dig att skicka in ett inlgg. Alternativt kan du blddra bland andra aktiva projekt fr att hitta ytterligare mjligheter till engagemang.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Hur redigerar eller raderar jag mitt inlgg?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Om du har lagt upp ditt inlgg men vill redigera eller radera det kan du hitta detta alternativ genom att klicka p de tre sm prickarna uppe till hger i inlgget.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Vilka r gemenskapens riktlinjer och modereringsprinciper?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Vra riktlinjer fr gemenskapen r till fr att se till att plattformen r ett skert utrymme fr alla att delta. Se till att dina inlgg r fria frn:</p><ul>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Personangrepp, frolmpningar, krnkande eller diskriminerande kommentarer</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Angrepp p sprket, inklusive svordomar</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Marknadsfrings- eller reklammaterial</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Personligt information om andra personer</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Upphovsrttsskyddat material, t.ex. bilder</li>\\n    </ul><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Inlgg eller kommentarer som inte fljer dessa riktlinjer kan komma att redigeras eller raderas, eller, i extrema fall, frhindras frn att publiceras. Ls vra villkor &amp; Villkor fr mer information.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Hur rapporterar jag ett sttande inlgg?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Klicka p de tre sm prickarna i det vre hgra hrnet av inlgget fr att rapportera det. Ange anledningen till att du rapporterar innehllet - detta kommer att skicka en anmlan s att inlgget kan granskas.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Varfr har jag svrt att registrera mig eller logga in?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Om du inte kan registrera dig kan det bero p att du redan har registrerat dig med samma e-postadress eller tidigare ftt en inbjudan att g med i plattformen. Om du ser ett meddelande om att din e-postadress r upptagen av en pgende inbjudan, kontrollera din e-post och flj lnken i inbjudan fr att registrera ditt konto. Om du inte hittar inbjudan kan du frska titta i din skrppostbox eller begra en ny inbjudan.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Hur terstller jag mitt lsenord?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Du kan alltid begra att f terstlla ditt lsenord frn inloggningssidan. Om du terstller ditt lsenord skickas en lnk till din e-postadress - flj instruktionerna fr att ndra ditt lsenord. Av skerhetsskl r lnken giltig i en timme. Om lnken har gtt ut kan du helt enkelt klicka p \\"Glmt lsenord?\\" p inloggningssidan igen fr att generera en ny terstllningslnk.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Om du inte fick e-postmeddelandet kan du kontrollera att det inte finns i din skrppost och att du skickar lnken till samma e-postadress som du registrerade dig med.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Vad kommer ni att gra med mina uppgifter?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Ls vr sekretesspolicy fr mer information om insamling och anvndning av uppgifter. I korthet kommer vi aldrig att anvnda dina uppgifter fr reklam, marknadsfring eller andra typer av skrppost.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Vilka e-postmeddelanden kommer jag att f?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Du kan f e-postmeddelanden som rr ditt konto och din aktivitet p plattformen, till exempel nr ngon svarar p ett av dina inlgg. Du kan styra vilka e-postmeddelanden du fr i dina instllningar. Det finns ett avsnitt som heter \\"Notiser\\" dr du kan aktivera och inaktivera e-postmeddelanden.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Hur raderar jag mitt konto?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">I dina instllningar finns det mjlighet att radera ditt konto. Inlgg som du har publicerat kommer att fortstta att publiceras, men ditt namn kommer att tas bort frn inlgget och ersttas med \\"oknd frfattare\\". Om du vill radera alla dina inlgg, gr det innan du raderar ditt konto.</p>", "tr-TR": "<h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Bu platformun oluturulma amac nedir?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Bu platform, bilgi paylamak, girdi ve geri bildirim almak iin ortak bir merkez olarak tasarlanmtr. Halihazrda aktif olan katlm projeleri ana sayfada gsterilir. Her katlm projesinin fikir eklemek, bir neri hakknda yorum yapmak, projeleri oylamak ve nceliklendirmek veya bir ankete katlmak gibi farkl bir katlm ekli olabilir.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Nasl katlabilirim?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Herkese ak projelere her zaman gz atabilirsiniz ancak bir ilem yapmak iin kaydolmanz gerekir. Bu, topluluk olma duygusunu korumaya ve girdilerin meruiyetini salamaya yardmc olur.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">nsanlar benimle ilgili hangi bilgileri grebilir?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Adnz, fotorafnz ve eer eklediyseniz biyografiniz grlr. Bu bilgileri Ayarlarnzdan deitirebilirsiniz.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Neden girdimi yaynlayamyorum veya yorum yapamyorum?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Yaynlama, yorum ve oylama, bir projenin yalnzca belirli zamanlarnda veya aamalarnda etkinletirilebilir. Baz durumlarda, bir proje yalnzca belirli bir payda grubunun katklarna ak olabilir.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Bir proje iin yaynlama o anda etkinse, yayn gndermenizi isteyen bir dme grrsnz. Alternatif olarak, dier katlm frsatlar iin dier aktif projelere gz atabilirsiniz.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Girdimi nasl dzenleyebilirim veya silebilirim?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Girdinizi yaynladysanz ancak dzenleme yapmak veya silmek istiyorsanz, yaynn sa st kesindeki  kk noktaya tklayarak bu seenei bulabilirsiniz.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Topluluk kurallar ve moderasyon politikalar nelerdir?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Topluluk kurallarmz, platformun herkesin katlabilecei gvenli bir alan olmasn salamay amalar. Ltfen yaynlarnzda aadakilerin bulunmadndan emin olun:</p><ul>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Kiisel saldrlar, hakaretler, kfrl veya ayrmc yorumlar</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Kfr dahil saldrgan dil</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Pazarlama veya reklam materyalleri</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Dier bireyler hakknda kiisel bilgiler</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Grseller gibi telifli materyaller</li>\\n  </ul><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Bu ynergelere uymayan tm yaynlar veya yorumlar dzenlenebilir, silinebilir ya da ok ar ihlallerde yaynlanmas engellenebilir. Daha fazla bilgi iin ltfen Hkm ve Koullarmz inceleyin.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Saldrgan bir yayn nasl ikayet edebilirim?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Bir yayn ikayet etmek iin yaynn sa st kesindeki  kk noktaya tklayn. Ltfen ierii ikayet etme nedeninizi belirtin. Bu ilem, yaynn incelenmesi iin bir bildirim gnderir.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Kaydolurken veya oturum aarken neden zorluk yayorum?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Kaydolamyorsanz, bunun nedeni ayn e-posta adresiyle zaten kaydolmu olmanz veya daha nce platforma katlmak iin bir davet alm olmanz olabilir. E-posta adresinizin bekleyen bir davet tarafndan alndn belirten bir mesaj grrseniz ltfen e-postanz kontrol edin ve hesabnz kaydetmek iin davetiyedeki balantya tklayn. Daveti bulamazsanz, spam kutunuza bakmay deneyin veya yeni bir davetiye isteyin.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Parolam nasl sfrlarm?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Oturum ama sayfasnda her zaman parolanz sfrlama talebinde bulunabilirsiniz. Parolanz sfrlarsanz e-posta adresinize bir balant gnderilir. Parolanz deitirmek iin talimatlar uygulayn. Gvenlik nedeniyle, bu balant bir saat sreyle geerli olur. Balantnn sresi dolduysa yeni bir sfrlama balants oluturmak iin oturum ama sayfasndaki \\"Parolanz m unuttunuz?\\" seeneine tekrar tklayabilirsiniz.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">E-postay almadysanz, spam kutunuzda olmadndan ve balanty kaydolduunuz e-posta adresine gnderdiinizden emin olun.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Verilerimle ne yapacaksnz?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Veri toplama ve kullanm hakknda daha fazla bilgi iin gizlilik politikamz inceleyin. Ksacas, verilerinizi asla reklam, pazarlama veya dier spam trleri iin kullanmayz.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Hangi e-postalar alacam?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Yaynlarnzdan birine yant verilmesi gibi, hesabnzla ve platformdaki etkinliinizle ilgili e-postalar alabilirsiniz. Hangi e-postalar alacanz Ayarlar blmnden kontrol edebilirsiniz. E-posta bildirimlerini ap kapatabileceiniz \\"Bildirimler\\" adl bir blm bulunmaktadr.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Hesabm nasl silebilirim?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Ayarlarnzda hesabnz silme seenei bulunmaktadr. Gnderdiiniz girdiler yaynlanmaya devam eder ancak adnz yayndan kaldrlr ve 'bilinmeyen yazar' ifadesi ile deitirilir. Tm girdilerinizi silmek istiyorsanz ltfen hesabnz silmeden nce yapn.</p>", "ur-PK": "<h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What is this platform for?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">This platform is designed as a central hub to share information and get input and feedback. Participation projects that are currently active are shown on the homepage - each participation project may have a different mode of engagement, whether its adding an idea, commenting on a proposal, voting on and prioritising projects, or taking a survey.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I participate?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">You can always browse public projects, but youll need to sign up in order to take an action. This helps to maintain a community feel and ensure the legitimacy of the input.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What information can people see about me?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Your name, photo and bio, if youve added one, are visible. You can always change these in your Settings.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Why cant I post my input or submit a comment?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Posting, commenting and voting may be enabled only during certain times or phases of a project. In some instances, a project may only be open to contributions from a certain stakeholder group.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">If posting is currently enabled for a project, youll see a button that prompts you to submit a post. Alternatively, you can browse other active projects for additional engagement opportunities.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I edit or delete my input?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">If youve posted your input but want to make edits or delete it, you can find this option by clicking on the three small dots on the top right of the post.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What are the community guidelines and moderation policies?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Our community guidelines are here to help ensure that the platform is a safe space for everyone to participate. Please ensure your posts are free of:</p><ul>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Personal attacks, insults, abusive or discriminatory comments</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Offensive language including profanity</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Marketing or advertising material</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Personal information about other individuals</li>\\n  <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Copyrighted material such as images</li>\\n  </ul><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Any posts or comments that do not adhere to these guidelines may be edited or deleted, or in extreme instances, prevented from being posted. Please review our Terms &amp; Conditions for more information.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I report an offensive post?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Click on the three small dots on the top right corner of the post to report it. Please indicate the reason you are reporting the content - this will send a notification for the post to be reviewed.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Why am I having difficulty signing up or logging in?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">If youre unable to sign up, it may be because youve already registered with the same email address or previously received an invitation to join the platform. If you see a message that your email address is taken by a pending invite, please check your email and follow the link in the invitation to register your account. If you cant find the invite, try looking in your spam box or request a new invitation.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I reset my password?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">You can always request to reset your password from the log in page. If you reset your password, a link will be sent to your email address - follow the instructions to change your password. For security reasons, the link is valid for one hour. If the link has expired, you can simply click on Forgot password? in the log in page again to generate a new reset link.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">If you didnt receive the email, check to make sure that its not in your spam and that youre sending the link to the same email address that you signed up with.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What will you do with my data?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Review our privacy policy for more information on data collection and usage. In short, we will never use your data for advertising, marketing or other types of spam.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">What emails will I receive?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">You may receive emails related to your account and your activity on the platform, for instance, when someone responds to one of your posts. You can control which emails you receive in your Settings. There is a section called Notifications where you can turn email notifications on and off.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">How do I delete my account?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">In your Settings there is the option to delete your account. Input that youve posted will remain published, but your name will be removed from the post and replaced with unknown author. If youd like to delete all of your input, please do so before deleting your account.</p>", "sr-Latn": "<h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">emu je namenjena ova platforma?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Platforma predstavlja centralno mesto za razmenu informacija i prikupljanje razliitih podataka i povratnih informacija. Participativni projekti koji su trenutno aktivni prikazani su na poetnoj stranici - svaki od njih moe da podrazumeva drugaiji nain uea, bilo da se radi o dodavanju nove ideje, komentarisanju predloga, glasanju i odreivanju prioriteta ili popunjavanja ankete.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Kako mogu da uestvujem?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">U svakom trenutku moete pregledati aktivne projekte, a ukoliko elite da uzmete uee u njima potrebno je da se registrujete. Ovo je potrebno kako bi se odrala zajednica i osigurala legitimnost dobijenih unosa.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Koje informacije o meni su vidljive javno?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Vidljivo je vae ime, fotografija i biografija - ukoliko ste je dodali. Ove informacije u svakom trenutku moete promeniti u svojim podeavanjima.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Zato ne mogu da objavim sadraj ili postavim komentar?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Objavljivanje, komentarisanje i glasanje je omoguceno samo tokom odreenog vremenskog intervala ili faze projekta. U nekim sluajevima, projekat moe biti otvoren samo za unose od strane odreene grupe korisnika.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Ukoliko je objavljivanje unosa u okviru odreenog projekta predvieno, videcete dugme koje omoguuje da unesete va sadraj. Takoe, moete pretraiti i ostale aktivne projekte kako biste pronali dodatne mogucnosti angaovanja.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Kako da izmenim ili obriem svoj unos?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Ako ste ve objavili unos, ali elite da ga izmenite ili izbriete, ovu opciju moete pronaci klikom na tri male take u gornjem desnom uglu objave.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Kakve su smernice za uee i politika moderiranja?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Cilj naih smernica je da pomognu da platforma bude bezbedan prostor za sve oblike uea. Zato vas molimo da vodite rauna o tome da vae objave ne sadre:</p><ul>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Line napade, uvrede, uvredljive ili diskriminiue komentare</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Uvredljiv ton, ukljuujuci i psovke</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Marketinki ili reklamni materijal</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Line podatke drugih pojedinaca</li>\\n    <li class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Materijal koji je zaticen autorskim pravima (poput fotografija)</li>\\n    </ul><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Bilo koje objave ili komentari koji se ne pridravaju ovih smernica mogu biti izmenjene ili obrisane, dok se u ekstremnim situacijama moe zabraniti i njihova objava. Molimo vas da pogledate naa Pravila i uslove za vie informacija.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Kako da prijavim uvredljiv sadraj?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Da biste prijavili ovakav sadraj, kliknite na tri male take u gornjem desnom uglu objave. Nakon toga, navedite razlog zbog kojeg prijavljujete sadraj  nakon ega e biti poslato obavetenje da se isti pregleda.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Zato imam potekoca sa registracijom ili prijavljivanjem?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Ako ne moete da se registrujete, razlog moe biti to to ste se ve registrovali sa istom email adresom ili vam je poziv za prikljuivanje platformi prethodno poslat. Ukoliko vidite obavetenje da je na vau email adresu ve poslat poziv koji je na ekanju, proverite svoju potu i kliknite na link u pozivnici kako biste registrovali nalog. Ukoliko ne moete da pronaete pozivnicu, proverite va spam folder ili zatraite da vam se poalje nova.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Kako da resetujem lozinku?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Resetovanje lozinke moete zatraiti putem stranice za prijavljivanje. Ukoliko resetujete lozinku, link ce biti poslat na vau email adresu, te je potrebno da sledite uputstva kako biste je promenili. Iz sigurnosnih razloga, link vai jedan sat. U sluaju da je link istekao, moete jednostavno da kliknete na opciju Zaboravili ste lozinku?, koja se nalazi na stranici za prijavljivanje, nakon ega e biti generisan novi link za resetovanje lozinke.</p><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Ukoliko niste dobili poruku, proverite da li se ona nalazi u vaoj spam poti, kao i da li ste prilikom zahtevanja linka uneli ispravnu email adresu.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">ta cete uiniti sa mojim podacima?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Proitajte nau politiku privatnosti za vie informacija o prikupljanju i koricenju podataka. Ukratko, nikada necemo koristiti vae podatke za oglaavanje, marketing ili druge vrste neeljene pote.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Koju vrstu email obavetenja u dobijati?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Moe se desiti da dobijete email obavetenja koja su povezana sa vaim nalogom i vaim aktivnostima na platformi  na primer, u situacijama u kojima neko odgovori na neku od vaih objava. U svojim podeavanjima, pod sekcijom Obavetenja moete ukljuiti i iskljuiti vrste poruka koje primate putem elektronske pote i tako odrediti koja email obavetenja elite da dobijate.</p><h2 class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">Kako da obriem svoj nalog?</h2><p class=\\"ql-align-justify\\">U vaim podeavanjima postoji mogucnost brisanja vaeg naloga. Sve vae prethodne objave i komentari e se i dalje nalaziti na platformi, ali e vae ime biti uklonjeno iz njih, odnosno zamenjeno sa ispisom nepoznati autor. Ako elite da izbriete i sve unose koje ste objavili, potrebno je da to uinite pre brisanja naloga.</p>"}	f	full_width_banner_layout	\N	\N	{}	no_button	\N	{}	{}	t	t	f	no_filter	f	f	{}	\N
